quran[903]{c,v,t}:
  17,1,"Gedha s Win Ibbwin amdan iS, d iminig n yiv, si Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ar Loamaâ ibaâden mavi, ideg Neôqa i as d izzin, iwakken ad as Nessken, seg issekniyen nne£. Ih, Neppa, d Win Isellen, Ipwalin"
  17,2,"Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, u Nerra p d nnhaya i At Isôail. \"Ur sâut awkil, war Nek"
  17,3,"D tarwa n wid i Nebbwi akked Nuê. Neppa, s tidep, d amdan isnemmiren"
  17,4,"Nsseyya di Tezmamt, i At Isôail: \"war ccekk, a ppesfesdem, di tmurt, berdayen, u aîas ara tesme$wôem iman nnwen"
  17,5,"Mi d iusa usefsed amenzu segsen, Nuzen awen d imdanen nne£, s loehd uqsiê, kecmen ixxamen; lemâahda tevôa"
  17,6,"Sinna, Nerra d ppaô nnwen, segsen. Nebbwi yawen d ayla, tarwa. Nesîuqqet iâsekôiwen nnwen"
  17,7,"Ma tmaânem, i iman nnwen, ma tdensem, i iman nnwen. Mi d tusa lemâahda taneggarut, ssexven udmawen nnwen, kecmen Loamaâ, akken i t kecmen abrid amenzu; hudden, wakali, ayen is ipzuxxun"
  17,8,"Ahat Mass nnwen ad Iêun fellawen. Ma tulsem, a Nales. Nerra Loahennama d lêebs i ijehliyen"
  17,9,"Ih, Leqwôan agi inehhu ar wayen iweqmen mavi, ibecceô lmumnin i ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar i nitni akafi meqqwôen"
  17,10,"Wanag wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, Nhegga yasen d aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  17,11,"Amdan issawal i cceôô, akken issawal i lxiô. Amdan izga d aêemmaq"
  17,12,"Nerra, iv akked wass, d sin issekniyen. Assekni n yiv Nerra d tellis, Nerra win n wass d win ipwalin, iwakken a pnadim lfevl n Mass nnwen, a ppissinem amvan iseggwasen, akked leêsab. Yal ta$awsa, Nfeûûel ip akken iwata"
  17,13,"I yal amdan, Ncudd as lbext is s amgarv is. Ass n tnekra, ad as d Nessuffe$ tazmamt ara iaf teldi"
  17,14,"£eô tazmamt ik! Tqaddev, assa, s yiman ik, i uqeîîi k"
  17,15,"Win ipwanhan, i iman is kan, win innetlafen, innetlaf mgal iman is kan. Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev. Ur Nekkat, alamma Nuzen amazan"
  17,16,"Ma Neb$a a Nesqucc tamdint, Neppak lameô i isâiyen is, ad xedmen, degs, cceôô. Ad iâaddi fellas Wawal, a p Nhudd wakali"
  17,17,"Acêal n tsuta ay Nesqucc, deffir Nuê! Ad Iqadd Mass ik, i tussna akked tmeéôiwt ibekkaven n imdanen iS"
  17,18,"Win ib$an taêemmaqt, Nezzazzal as degs, i £ ihwan, i win i £ Neb$a. Sinna, Nerra yas Loahennama ad din iô$, indell, ippuveggeô"
  17,19,"Win ib$an laxeôt, iaâzem fellas yal laâzem, u neppa iumen; widak, tajmilt i laâzem nnsen"
  17,20,"I akw, i wigi d wiyav, Nwessaâ tikci s$uô Mass ik. Tikci n Mass ik, ur meêdudet"
  17,21,"Wali amek Nesmenyaf kra i wiyav. War ccekk, di laxeôt, lfeôq d usmenyef, ad ilin sennig waya"
  17,22,"Ur sâu, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, mulac a ppu$alev d imdelli, d imveggaâ"
  17,23,"Iseyya d Mass ik: ur tâabdem siwa Neppa, elhut ar imawlan. Ma, $uôek wesser yiwen, ne$ ma wessren i sin, ur asen qqaô: \"ttfuh\"! Ur ten ppara. Mmeslay asen s lkyasa"
  17,24,"Zger fellasen tacvat n lmaênana. Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ëun fellasen, akken iyi d ssekren d amejtuê"
  17,25,"Mass nnwen Yif akw akken Issen, i illan deg iman nnwen. Ma telham, Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê wid isteôoiâen"
  17,26,"Efk i llezm ik amur is, akw i ume$bun akked win d ibbwi ubrid. Ur pjeggiê d ajeggeê"
  17,27,"Ijeggaêen, s tidep, d atmaten n Cciîan. Cciîan ijhel ar Mass is"
  17,28,"Ma tfuôqev ten, tôe$bev u tegguniv aêunu s$uô Mass ik, ini yasen awal aéidan"
  17,29,"Ur pcuddu afus ik ar yiri k, ur as berru aîas, mulac a ppu$alev d ambaûi, d ame$bun"
  17,30,"S tidep, Mass ik I$ennu win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali, Issen imdanen iS"
  17,31,"Ur Neqqet arraw nnwen, ma tugadem tiggulelt. D Nekwni ara ten Iôezqen, kunwi yidsen. Ih, timen$iwt nnsen d tucmip meqqwôen"
  17,32,"Ur zennut, d ayen n dir, d abrid ucmit"
  17,33,"Ur neqqet amdan i wen Igdel Öebbi, siwa ma di tidep. Win ipwan$an s le$deô, ihi, a Nefk adabu i walag is. Ur ipjuôôu di tmen$iwt, ihi, neppa, ad ippusellek"
  17,34,"Ur pnalet ayla ugujil, siwa ar wayen imaânen, ar d immeêtel. Qadôet lemâahda; ih, lemâahda s usteqsi"
  17,35,"Qadôet lkil ma tektalem, weznet s lmizan imaânen. Yif it wakka, a ppelhu taggara"
  17,36,"Ur îîafaô ayen ur tessinev. Timejjin, iéôi, ul, s tidep, ad ppuseqsin akw"
  17,37,"Ur teddu di tmurt, d amzuxxi. Ih, keçç ur tezmirev, d awez$i, a pneqôev tamurt, ne$ a ppessiwvev laâli idurar"
  17,38,"Adiran, deg waya akw, Ikerh it Mass ik"
  17,39,"Ayagi, seg wayen i k Iweêêa Mass ik, n ûûwab. Ur ppara, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, mulac a ppepwaveggôev ar Loahennama d ambaûi, d amnafeq"
  17,40,"Day wen d Ifren Mass nnwen arrac, u Iddem, i iman iS, tullas, si lmalayek? S tidep, kunwi tegrem d awal anecilat"
  17,41,"Ih, ay d Nebbwi di Leqwôan agi, iwakken a d mmektin. I yasen d irna, siwa a$unfu"
  17,42,"Ini: \"lemmer llin yides iôebbiten, akken la d qqaôen, yili ad nadin abrid ara ten iawin ar n Bab n usgeld"
  17,43,"Gedha s yiS, aîas i Aâlay sennig wayen d qqaôen"
  17,44,"Ppanzen aS igenwan di ûa, tamurt, u wayen illan degsen. Ur illi wayen ur aS neppanez, ur T Nesbuccuâ s ccekôan. Maca, ur tfehmem ara annuz nnsen. Ih, Neppa Iêellem, Ipsemmiê"
  17,45,"Mara teqqaôev Leqwôan, Neppara, garak d wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, aêurrim abavni"
  17,46,"Nerra $ef ulawen nnsen ssteô, iwakken ur t fehmen; di tmejjin nnsen, tiâéegt. Ma tesmektiv d, di Leqwôan, Mass ik d Yiwen, ad zzin akin, s u$unfu"
  17,47,"Nekwni, Nif akw akken Neéôa, acu iwumi sellen, mara k ssemêasen, mara hedôen, mi qqaôen imednas: \"la teppeddum kan d urgaz iwumi sseêren"
  17,48,Wali amek i k d bbwin imedyaten. Nnetlafen. Ur zmiren ad afen abrid
  17,49,"Nnan: \"day mi nu$al d i$san, d a$webbaô, d ûûeê a d nu$al di lxelq amaynut"
  17,50,"Ini: \"ilit d azôu ne$ d uzzal"
  17,51,"ne$ d lxelq id iusan deg idmaren nnwen\". A d inin: \"anwa ara a $ d irren\"? Ini: \"d Win ikwen id Ixelqen, abrid amenzu\". Ad huzen iqweôôa nnsen $uôek, ad inin: \"melmi ayagi\"? Ini: \"izmer ad yili iqeôb ed"
  17,52,"Ass ideg ara awen d Isiwel, a d tjawbem s ccekôan iS, a p$ilem cwiî kan ay teqqimem"
  17,53,"Ini i imdanen iw ad inin awal ifuqen. Cciîan, s tidep, isskar ameôéi garasen. Ih, Cciîan d acengu n ûûeê i umdan"
  17,54,"Mass nnwen Yif akw akken ikwen Issen. Ad Iêun fellawen, ma Ib$a; a kwen Iâaqeb ma Ib$a. Ur k id Nuzen ara d awkil nnsen"
  17,55,Mass ik Yif akw akken Iéôa i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Ni$ Nesmenyaf kra n lambiyya i wiyav. I Dawed Nefka Ihellilen
  17,56,"Ini: \"nujet $eô wid tepkabarem, war Neppa. Ur zmiren ad awen kksen ccqa, ne$ a t bedlen"
  17,57,"Wigi u$uô la pnujun, la pqelliben ppawil ara ten isqeôben nezzeh ar Mass nnsen. Ssaramen aêunu S, ppagwaden aâaqeb iS\". Ih, aâaqeb n Mass ik, issagwad"
  17,58,"Ur telli temdint ur Nesquccu, uqbel ass n tnekra, ne$ ur Nâaqeb s leqseê. Ayagi iura di Tezmamt"
  17,59,"I £ iîîfen $ef uceggaâ issekniyen, d nnkeô nnsen, kan, s$uô imezwura. Nuzen ed tal$wemt i Tamud, d ayen pwalin. Densen p. Ur d Neppazen issekniyen siwa i ussigwed"
  17,60,"Mi k Nenna: \"Mass ik, s tidep, Izzi i imdanen\". Ma dayen i k Nerra teéôiv t, d ahewwel kan i medden. Akken ttejôa tamenâult di Leqwôan. Nessagwad iten. Ay sen d irennu siwa nnfaq ameqwôan"
  17,61,"Mi Nenna i lmalayek: \"knumt i Adem\", knant, siwa Iblis. Inna: \"day ad knu$ i win Txelqev s talaxt"
  17,62,"Inna: \"Twalav wagi i Tâuzzev sennig iw, lemmer a yi Teooev, ar ass n tnekra, war ccekk, ad $wu$ tarwa s, siwa ixeîîayen"
  17,63,"Inna: \"Öuê! Wid, segsen, i iddan yidek, ihi, aqeîîi nnwen d Loahennama, d aqeîîi meqqwôen"
  17,64,"Laâaj win iwumi tzemôev, degsen, s ta$wect ik. £ewwes fellasen s imnayen ik, d iterrasen ik. Ecrek yidsen ayla, tarwa. Âahed asen\". I yasen iâahed Cciîan, siwa a$uôôu"
  17,65,"Ma d imdanen iW, ur tesâiv adabu fellasen\". Mass ik Iqadd d Awkil"
  17,66,"Mass nnwen, i wen Isselêayen lbabuô di yill, a pnadim lfevl iS. Ih, Neppa Ipêunu fellawen"
  17,67,"Ma tevôa yidwen lmuûiba di yill, ayen u$uô tepnujum, war Neppa, ittellif. Mi kwen Isellek ar lberr, twexxôem. Amdan izga d lkaraâ"
  17,68,"Day t$ilem ur Ipseggix ara tamurt yiswen, ne$ ur awen d Ippazen ara tabucivant, d$a ur teppafem awkil"
  17,69,"Ne$ day t$ilem ur kwen id Ippara ara tikelt nniven, ad awen d Iazen aûeôûaô, a kwen I$mes ilmend n tijehli nnwen, sinna ur teppafem, mgal a£, amalal"
  17,70,"Ni$ Nkeyyes tarwa n Adem. Nebbwi ten di lberr, di yill, N$at iten s wayen ilhan, Nesmenyaf iten, nezzeh, i waîas seg wid i Nexleq"
  17,71,"Ass ideg ara Nenced akw imdanen, s imvebôen nnsen; win id tusa tezmamt is yeffus is, widak ad $ôen tazmamt nnsen, ur pwadensen s tissegnit"
  17,72,"win illan d ader$al di tagi, ad yili d ader$al di laxeôt, ad izid di tuff$a n ubrid"
  17,73,"S tidep, qôib i k hewwlen $ef wayen i k d Nweêêa, a d tesnulfuv ayen nniven, mgal a£. D$a, a k rren d aêbib"
  17,74,"Lemmer ur k Ntebbet ara, qôib tmalev cwiî $uôsen"
  17,75,"Yili ad ak Nesâaddi tudert akked tmeppant, berdayen, sinna, ur teppafev, mgal a£, w ara k isellken"
  17,76,"Ih, qôib i k id srewlen si tmurt, a k id ssuff$en segs. Yili cwiî kan ara d gwrin, deffir ek"
  17,77,"D tannumi imazanen nne£, id Nuzen, uqbel ik. Ur teppafev ara abeddel, di lâadda nne£"
  17,78,"Bedd i téallit mi istu$la yiîij, alamma d tellis n yiv. Leqwôan, tafrara. Ih, Leqwôan, tafrara, isâa inagan"
  17,79,"Aâwez yis kra n yiv, d nnafila k, amar a k id Irr Mass ik, deg umkan i pcekkiôen"
  17,80,"Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ssekcem iyi, anekcum n tidep. Ssuffe$ iyi, tuff$a n tidep. Efk iyi, s$uôeK, adabu ipselliken"
  17,81,"Ini: \"tusa d tidep, $abent tkerkas. Ih, tikerkas ilaq ad $abent"
  17,82,"Nesrusu d, si Leqwôan, ayen illan d êellu akked uêunu i lmumnin. I irennu, i imednas, siwa lexsaôa"
  17,83,"Ma N$at amdan ad iwexxeô, ad iveôôef iman is. Ma iêuza t wugur ad iayes"
  17,84,"Ini: \"yal yiwen ixeddem akken ipwali. Mass nnwen Yif akw akken i Issen anwa i ipwanhan kteô"
  17,85,"Steqsan k id $ef ôôuê. Ini: \"ôôuê si lameô n Mass iw. Drus kan n tmusni i wen ippunefken"
  17,86,"Ma ihwa ya£, a Nekkes ayen i k Nweêêa. D$a ur teppafev, mgal a£, awkil"
  17,87,"siwa aêunu s$uô Mass ik. Ih, lfevl iS, i keçç, izga meqqweô"
  17,88,"Ini: \"lemmer ad mlilen imdanen akked leonun, iwakken a d awin am Leqwôan agi, ur d ppawin i t icban, xas mâawanen"
  17,89,"Ni$ Nefka d i imdanen, di Leqwôan agi, si yal imedyaten. Tegwti n yimdanen ur b$in, siwa tijehli"
  17,90,"Nnan: \"ur k neppamen alamma tesfeggvev a$ d a$balu, si tmurt"
  17,91,"ne$, tesâiv leonan n tezdayin akked tfeôôant, ideg feggven isaffen"
  17,92,"ne$, a d tesse$liv igenni d ifeûlan, akken i $ tzuxxev; ne$, a d tasev s Öebbi akked lmalayek, zdat nne"
  17,93,"Ne$ a ppesâuv axxam imzewweq, ne$ a ppaliv s igenni. Ur neppamen, s walluy ik, alamma tessersev ane$ d tazmamt ara n$eô\". Ini: \"gedha s Mass iw! Day lli$ d ayen nniven, siwa d amdan amazan"
  17,94,"I iîîfen imdanen ur uminen, mi ten id tusa nnhaya, mara d inin kan: \"Iuzen ed Öebbi amdan d amazan"
  17,95,"Ini: \"lemmer llint, di tmurt, lmalayek, teddunt di laman, yili Nessers asent ed, seg igenni, lmelk amazan"
  17,96,"Ini: \"Iqadd Mass iw d Anagi, gari yidwen. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali imdanen iS, Issen iten"
  17,97,"Win Inha Öebbi, atan idda d ubrid. Wid Itlef, ur asen teppafev imawlan, war Neppa, d awez$i. A ten id Nefser ass n tnekra $ef udmawen nnsen, dre$len, gugmen, âaégen. Axxam nnsen d Loahennama. Mi tenqes tmes, ad asen Nernu ajajiê"
  17,98,"D wagi ay d aqeîîi nnsen, imi nekôen issekniyen nne£, u nnan: \"day mi nu$al d i$san, d a$webbaô, a d nu$al di lxelq amaynut"
  17,99,"Ne$, day ur walan ara ar Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, Izmer a d Ixleq i ten icban? Irra yasen lajel, ur degs ccekk. Ur b$in imednas, siwa tijehli"
  17,100,"Ini: \"lemmer tesâim igerrujen uêunu n Mass iw, ur ten tepnalem, a ppagwadem a ten tûeôôfem. Amdan izga d imceêêi"
  17,101,"Ni$ Nefka, i Musa, tza issekniyen iberrzen. Steqsi At Isôail. Mi d iusa $uôsen, inna yas Ferâun: \"a Musa! Nek, wala$, war ccekk, seêêern ak"
  17,102,"Inna: \"ni$ teéôiv ur d issers yiwen wigi, d tiftilin, siwa Mass n tmurt akked igenwan. Nek, wala$, a Ferâun, war ccekk, tîeêênev"
  17,103,"Ib$a a ten iééaâ si tmurt, N$emmeq it, akked wid iddan yides, meôôa"
  17,104,"Deffir es, Nenna i At Isôail: \"zed$et tamurt. Mi d tusa lemâahda n laxeôt, a kwen id Nawi, d îayfat"
  17,105,"Nessers it id s tidep. S tidep, ay d irs. Nuzen ik id, kan, i ubecceô d uneddeô"
  17,106,"Leqwôan Nfeôq it, iwakken a t temlev i medden, s laâqel. Nessader it id, s l$eôv"
  17,107,"Ini: \"amnet yis, ne$ qqimet\". Ih, ma mlan t i wid tebbwev tussna, uqbel is, ad $lin $ef udmawen, knan"
  17,108,"Ad inin: \"gedha s Mass nne$! Tûaô lemâahda n Mass nne"
  17,109,Ad $lin $ef udmawen s imeîîawen. Ad innerni wannuz nnsen
  17,110,"Ini: \"nujet $er Öebbi, ne$ nujet $er Uênin. Akken tnujem, ineS ismawen imaânen yifen akw wiyav\". Di téallit ik, ur saâlay ûûut ik, ur t ssrusu. Ad isker kan"
  17,111,"Ini: \"ccekôan i Öebbi, ur Nesâi aqcic, ur Nesâi acrik di tgelda, ur Nesâi bab mgal asdullu\". Ssem$weô iT yal tem$weô"
  18,1,"Ccekôan i Öebbi, id Issersen Tazmamt, i uxdim iS. Aâwaj, degs, ur Irri"
  18,2,"Tewqem, iwakken a ppâaggen $ef ssxev uwâiô, s$uôeS; u a pbecceô lmumnin ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar nnsen warraz igerzen"
  18,3,"Ad ilin degs, i lebda"
  18,4,"A ppâaggen i wid innan: \"Öebbi Isâa mmi S"
  18,5,"Ur illi wayen ssnen fellas; akken, imezwura nnsen. D awal uqbiê id iff$en seg imawen nnsen. D tikerkas kan ay ssawalen"
  18,6,"Ahat a phelkev iman ik, ar loiha nnsen, a p$weblev, imi ur uminen ara s usali agi"
  18,7,"Ni$ Nerra i illan di tmurt, d ccbaêa ines, iwakken a Néeô menyif iten, ar igiten ilhan"
  18,8,"A Nu$al a Nerr, i illan degs, d akal ibuôen"
  18,9,"Ne$ t$ilev d At yifri kan, akked Öaqim, ay d lwehma, ger issekniyen nne£"
  18,10,"Mi ssôen iman nnsen ilmeéiyen deg ifri, nnan: \"a Mass nne$! Efk ane$ d aêunu s$uôeK; Err a$ lameô nne$ d uûwib"
  18,11,"Deg ifri, Nesle$ imeééu$en nnsen, acêal iseggwasen"
  18,12,"Sinna, Nessker iten id, a Néeô anta, ger snat n trebbuyaâ, i iêesben acêal qqimen"
  18,13,"Nekwni, ad ak Neêku, s tidep, taqsiî nnsen. Nitni, ih, d ilmeéiyen, umnen s Mass nnsen. Nerna yasen nnhaya"
  18,14,"Nesseohed ulawen nnsen, mi kren nnan: \"Mass nne$ d Mass n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur nepnuju, d awez$i, ar ôebbi, war Neppa, mulac a d nini awal dduni"
  18,15,"Widak d agdud nne$. Âabden iôebbiten, war Neppa. Ay$eô ur a$ d bbwin, fellasen, adabu n ûûeê? Anwa i idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi"
  18,16,"Mi ten tfuôqem, nitni akked wayen âabden war Öebbi, essôet iman nwen deg ifri. Ad awen Izraâ, Mass nnwen, seg uêunu S. Ad awen Iheggi amwanes i lameô nnwen"
  18,17,"A pwaliv iîij, mi d inqeô, iwexxeô i ifri nnsen, ar yeffus. Mi i$li, ad asen iâaddi $eô zelmev. Nitni, din, di littsaâ. Ayagi seg issekniyen n Öebbi. Win Inha Öebbi, neppa ipwanha; win Itlef, ur isâi, d awez$i, bab ara t inhun"
  18,18,"Ad as tiniv ukin, nitni îîsen. Ntezzi ten yeffus, zelmev. Aydi nnsen, $ef umnaô, iééel ivaôen is. Lemmer a ten twaliv, ad asen trewlev, si tugdi; a k terkeb, segsen, lefqaâ"
  18,19,"Akka ay ten id Nessenker, iwakken ad mesteqsin. Inna yiwen segsen: \"acêal n lweqt ay tesâaddam\"? Nnan d: \"nesâadda ass ne$ ur ibbwiv wass\". Nnan: \"Mass nnwen Yif akw akken Izôa ay tesâaddam. Aznet ar temdint, yiwen segwen, s idrimen agi nnwen. Ad iwali anwa lqut iûfan mavi, ad awen d iawi ôôeéq, segs. Ad iêader iman is, iwakken ur awen ipfaq yiwen"
  18,20,"Nitni, war ccekk, ma éôan kwen, a kwen ôeomen, ne$ a kwen rren ar ddin nnsen, d$a ur trebêen, d awez$i"
  18,21,"Akka ay sen ten Nessken, iwakken ad éôen ar lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep; u, $ef yimir, ur illi ccekk. Mi mqellaân $ef lameô nnsen, nnan: \"bnut axxam sennig sen. Mass nnsen Yif akw akken iten Issen\". Nnan wid iwumi iâadda wawal, $ef lameô nnsen: \"a nerr, ihi, lemqam sennig sen"
  18,22,"Ad inin: \"di krav yidsen, aydi nnsen d wis kué\"; u ad inin: \"di semus yidsen, aydi nnsen d wis sdis\", pqelliben tabavnit. U ad inin: \"di ûa yidsen, aydi nnsen d wis îam\". Ini: \"Mass iw Yif akw akken Iéôa amvan nnsen. Drus kan i t iéôan\". Ur pnamar fellasen, siwa $ef wayen id ivehôen. Ur ppesteqsay yiwen fellasen"
  18,23,"Ur qqaô ta$awsa a p xedme$, s tidep, azekka"
  18,24,"siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Mmekti d Mass ik, ma teppuv. Ini: \"amar ad iyi Inhu Mass iw, ar wayen yifen ayagi di ûûwab"
  18,25,"Sâaddan, deg ifri nnsen, krav twinas iseggwasen, rnan tza nniven"
  18,26,"Ini: \"Öebbi Yif akw akken Iéôa, acêal sâaddan. IneS tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. Amek Neppa Ipwali, Isell! Ur sâin bab, war Neppa. Ur Izdukkul yiwen i useyyi S"
  18,27,"Mel ayen ik ed ippuweêêan, si Tezmamt n Mass ik. Ur illi ubeddel deg wawal iS. Ur teppafev ssôan, war Neppa, d awez$i"
  18,28,"Üebbeô iman ik, akked wid ipnujun ar Mass nnsen, taûebêit, tameddit, pnadin udem iS. Ur ten tekkes si ger wallen ik, a pvemâav lefnun n tmeddurt n ddunit. Ur ssemêas i win iwumi Nesse$fel ul is, ar usmekti nne£, i iddan d lhawiyya s, iwumi iffuhri lameô"
  18,29,"Ini: \"tidep s$uô Mass nnwen. Ad iamen win ib$an, ad ijhel win ib$an\". Ih, Nhegga d times, i imednas; ad asen zzin iêeoouoa s. Ma ppren d, ad asen ppunefken waman am uzzal ifsin. Ad cwin wudmawen nnsen. A tissit tamcumt, a tanezdu$t tucmip"
  18,30,"Ih, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, s tidep, ur Nveggiâ akafi n win ixedmen ayen ilhan"
  18,31,"I wigi, leonanat n Âaden, ddaw sen isaffen ppazzalen. Ad qqnen, dinna, imeqyasen n ddheb, ad lsen iceîîiven izegzawen n leêrir, êewcen s ddheb. Ad élen, degs, $ef imîeôêen izewwqen. A lebsa lâali, a tanezdu$t tumâint"
  18,32,"Awi yasen d amedya n sin irgazen. I yiwen, Nefka snat tebêirin n téuôin, Nezzi yasent tizdayin, Nerra iger garasent"
  18,33,"Yal tibêirt teppak ed l$ella s, ur ipxuûûu, segs, wacemma. Nesfeggev asif garasent"
  18,34,"I$ellet ed ppemôa. Inna i umdakwel is, mi s immeslay: \"$elbe$ k taôkunt, iffe$ k alag"
  18,35,"Idens iman is mi ikcem leonan is, inna: \"ur cukke$ ara, d awez$i, ad iqucc wayagi"
  18,36,"Ur cukke$ ara ad yili yimir, u ma bbwve$ ar Mass iw, ard affe$, war ccekk, ayen yifen aya, deg umekkan is"
  18,37,"Inna yas umdakwel is, mi s immeslay: \"day tnekôev Win ik Ixelqen seg wakal, sinna, si tiqqit, sinna, Imessel ik d argaz"
  18,38,"Maca, Neppa d Öebbi, Mass iw. Ur pcarake$ yiwen, i Mass iw"
  18,39,"Lemmer id tenniv, mi tkecmev ar tebêirt ik: akken Irad Öebbi. Ur telli tezmert siwa s$uô Öebbi. Ma twalav iyi d, nek, tifev iyi ayla, tarwa"
  18,40,"Izmer Mass iw ad iyi d Ifk ayen i ifen tibêirt ik. A d Iazen $uôes ssxev, seg igenni, a ppu$al d aêecraruf issiccigen"
  18,41,"ne$, ad zzren waman is, ur ten teppafev, d awez$i"
  18,42,"Tqucc l$ella s. D$a la izeyyeô ifassen is, $ef wayen iseôôef fellas. Tqucc tfeôôant is. Inna: \"a yamxix iw, a lemmer ur curke$ yiwen, i Mass iw"
  18,43,"Ur as illi urbaâ ara t isellken, war Öebbi. Ur isellek iman is"
  18,44,"Akka, laânaya s$uô Öebbi, Tidep. Yif akw i ukafi, Yif akw i taggara"
  18,45,"Awi yasen d amedya n tmeddurt n ddunit. Am aman id Nesse$li seg igenni. Eâluâlen yissen im$an n tmurt. D$a u$alen d asa$uô, issebruzzaâ iten wavu. Ni$ Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  18,46,"Ayla akked dderya d ccbaêa n tmeddurt n ddunit. Ar Mass ik, leûlaê idumen ifen ten i ukafi, ifen ten i tmeôoiwt"
  18,47,"Ass ideg ara Nesselêu idurar, a pwaliv tamurt d aza$aô. A ten Nefser, ur Neppaoa yiwen segsen"
  18,48,"A d rsen zdat Mass ik, d leûfuf: \"ni$ tusam a£ d, akken ikwen Nexleq tikelt tamenzut. Irna tetebbtem ar ur awen Neppara ppaâud, d awez$i"
  18,49,"Ters ed Tezmamt. A pwaliv ibe$wviyen s uêebbiô, $ef wayen illan degs. Qqaôen: \"a yamxix nne$! Acimi tazmamt agi ur teooi ayen meééiyen, u wayen meqqwôen, armi ten teêseb\"? Ufan illa wayen xedmen. Mass ik ur Idennis yiwen"
  18,50,"Mi Nenna i lmalayek: \"knumt i Adem\", knant, siwa Iblis. Neppa, si leonun, iaâûa lameô n Mass is. Day a ten terrem, neppa akked tarwa s, d imawlan, war Nek? U nitni d icenga nnwen! D abdil ucmit n imednas"
  18,51,"Ur ten Rri$ d inagan n lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan, ne$ n lxelq nnsen. Ur Ïîife$ im$eôôqen d imâiwnen"
  18,52,"Ass ideg ara d Yini: \"neccdet wid iyI terram d icriken iW\". Ad asen siwlen, ur asen d pparan. Nerra, garasen, asif n twa$it"
  18,53,"Ibe$wviyen ad walin times. ÊëËûan ar nitni, degs, ara $lin. Ur ppafen, segs, tisensert"
  18,54,"Ni$ Nefka d, di Leqwôan agi, yal amedya, i imdanen. Maca, ipnamar umdan sennig akw"
  18,55,"D acu i iîîfen imdanen ad amnen, mi ten id tusa nnhaya, u ad ste$fôen Mass nnsen? Ar ten id tas kan, tin ivôan d imezwura, ne$ ar d irs, zdat sen, uâaqeb"
  18,56,"Ur Neppazen imazanen, siwa i ubecceô d uneddeô. Wid ijehlen pnamaren, s tkerkas, îîeggiôen yissent tidep. Pmaâliken $ef issekniyen iW, akked wayen i$ef ppunedôen"
  18,57,"Anwa idensen sennig win iwumi d pwafekkôen issekniyen n Mass is, iwexxeô asen, u ippu i ixdem ufus is. Ih, Nerra aêurrim $ef wulawen nnsen, ur t fehhmen; akked tiâéegt deg imeééu$en nnsen. Ma tneccdev ten ar nnhaya, ur pwanhan, d awez$i"
  18,58,"Mass ik Ipsemmiêen, d Bab uêunu. Lemmer ad Iêud fellasen ilmend n wayen kesben, ad I$iwel ar uâaqeb nnsen. Maca, sâan ppaâud, ur ppafen segs tisensert"
  18,59,"Timdinin nni i Nesqucc mi densent, Nga ppaâud i usquccu nnsent"
  18,60,"Mi inna Musa i uqeddac is: \"ur êebbse$ alamma bbwve$ ar umlili n sin ilellen, xas ad sâaddi$ tallit"
  18,61,"Mi bbwven ar umlili nnsen, ppun aslem nnsen. Iu$al ar yill d ilelli"
  18,62,"Mi zegren, inna i uqeddac is: \"awi a$ d imekli nne$, ni$ naâteb deg inig nne$ agi"
  18,63,"Inna: \"ur twalav ara, mi nreyyeê ar teéôut, nek ppu$ en aslem? D Cciîan kan iyi isseppun ur ak nni$. Ibbwi abrid is ar yill, d lwehma"
  18,64,"Inna: \"d ayagi ay neb$a\". D$a u$alen d $ef isurifen nnsen"
  18,65,"Ufan d amdan seg imdanen nne£, iwumi Nefka aêunu s$uône£. Neslemd as tussna i illan $uône£"
  18,66,"Inna yas Musa: \"Ma ad ddu$ yidek, ad iyi tesêefvev ay tesnev n ûûwab"
  18,67,"Inna d: \"keçç, s tidep, ur tezmiôev, yidi, a pûebôev"
  18,68,Amek ara tûebôev i wayen i$ef ur tesâiv asali
  18,69,"Inna: \"ad iyi tafev, ma Irad Öebbi, d aûebôi. Ur pnaqwame$ lameô ik"
  18,70,"Inna: \"ma teddiv yidi, ur iyi d steqsay $ef wacemma, alamma smekti$ k id fellas"
  18,71,"Lêan, armi rekben di lbabuô. Ixeôq it. Inna: \"txeôqev t, iwakken ad $evûen l$aci s! Ni$ ayen txedmev d dduni"
  18,72,"Inna: \"day ur ak nni$ ara, keçç, s tidep, ur tezmiôev, yidi, a pûebôev, d awez$i"
  18,73,"Inna: \"ur iyi pqasa imi ppu$, ur ssukku lwaâôan $ef lameô iw"
  18,74,"Lêan, armi d mmugren ileméi. In$a t. Inna: \"ten$iv amdan ur nen$i yiwen! Ni$ d ayen idensen ay txedmev"
  18,75,"Inna: \"day ur ak nni$ ara, keçç, s tidep, ur tezmiôev, yidi, a pûebôev, d awez$i"
  18,76,"Inna: \"ma steqsa$ k $ef t$awsa, deffir ta, ur teddu yidi. Ni$ ssutre$ ak d ssmaê"
  18,77,"Lêan, armi bbwven ar imezda$ n yiwet n temdint, ssutren asen lqut. Ugin a ten snubgten. Ufan en lêiv, qôib ad i$li. Iûeggem it. Inna: \"ma teb$iv, tzemrev a ppepwaxellûev $ef waya"
  18,78,"Inna: \"Tura a nemfaôaq. Ad ak d fke$ lmaâna n wayen i$ef ur tezmirev a pûebôev, d awez$i"
  18,79,"Lbabuô nni, n igellilen i ixedmen di yill. B$i$ a t ôée$, acku yiwen ugellid, deffir sen, itekkes yal lbabuô, s yi$il"
  18,80,"Wanag ileméi nni, llan imawlan is d lmumnin. Nugad ad iêeppem fellasen tinufqa, tijehli"
  18,81,"Neb$a ad asen d Irr, Mass nnsen, it yifen: win iûfan, iqeôben nezzeh aêunu"
  18,82,"Wanag lêiv, n sin warrac igujilen n temdint. Illa ugerruj seddaw as, i nitni. Babat sen d argaz ilhan. Mass ik Ib$a, ard im$uôen, ara d ssuff$en agerruj nnsen. D aêunu s$uô Mass ik. Ur t xdime$ s lameô iw. D tagi ay d lmaâna n wayen i$ef ur tezmiôev a pûebôev"
  18,83,"Steqsan k $ef Bu sin wacciwen. Ini: \"ad awen d awi$, fellas, asmekti"
  18,84,"S tidep, Nefka yas di tmurt, u Nsehhel as iberdan di yal cci"
  18,85,Iîîef yiwen n ubrid
  18,86,"armi sanda i$elli yiîij. Iufa i$elli $ef tala ilu$en. Iufa n $uôes agdud. Nenna: \"a Bu sin wacciwen, âaqeb iten, ne$ lhu $uôsen"
  18,87,"Inna: \"win idensen a t nâaqeb, sinna, ad iu$al ar Mass is at Iâaqeb aâaqeb unekkaô"
  18,88,"Wanag i win iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, akafi igerzen. Ad as Nini i isehlen si lameô nne£"
  18,89,"Sinna, ilêa d yiwen n ubrid"
  18,90,"armi sanda d ineqqeô yiîij. Iufa n ineqqeô ed $ef ugdud, iwumi ur Nefki ar at isdarin segs"
  18,91,Am akka. Ni$ ibbwev a£ d akw usali s
  18,92,"Sinna, idda d yiwen n ubrid"
  18,93,"armi ibbwev ger sin iêdiden. Iufa, deffir sen, agdud qôib ur fehhmen awal"
  18,94,"Nnan: \"a Bu sin wacciwen, s tidep, Iaouo akked Maouo la ssefsaden di tmurt. A k nxelleû ma terriv ûûuô garane$ yidsen"
  18,95,"Inna: \"yif it iyi Ifka Mass iw. Efket iyi afus, ad rre$ ûûuô garawen yidsen"
  18,96,"Awit iyi d tiqaùmtin n wuzzal alamma irgel wayen illan ger idurar\". Inna: \"ûuvet alamma tekker degs tmes. Awit iyi d ad smire$ fellas nnêas ifsin"
  18,97,"D$a ur zmiren a t id zegren, ur zmiren a t id flun"
  18,98,"Inna: \"ayagi d aêunu s$uô Mass iw. Mi d tusa lemâahda n Mass iw, a t Isawi. Lemâahda n Mass iw d tidep"
  18,99,"Assen, a ten Neoo ad ddehmen wa $ef wa. Aûuvu di lbuq, d$a a ten Nessemlil akw"
  18,100,"A d Nessken nezzeh Loahennama, assen, i ijehliyen"
  18,101,"wid iwumi sêurrment wallen nnsen, mgal asmekti W. Llan ur zmiren i usemêes"
  18,102,"Day $ilen, wid ijehlen, ad rren imdanen iW, d imawlan war Nek? Ih, Nhegga Loahennama, d axxam i ijehliyen"
  18,103,"Ini: \"ad awen mle$ at igiten imexsuôen sennig wiyav"
  18,104,"Wid iwumi iweddeô laâtab nnsen di tmeddurt n ddunit, wanag nitni nwan gerzen igi"
  18,105,"Widak d wid i inekôen issekniyen n Mass nnsen, akked temlilit yideS. Mêan igiten nnsen. Ur ten Nwezzen, ass n tnekra"
  18,106,"Atan uqeîîi nnsen: Loahennama, imi jehlen, u mmaâlken deg issekniyen iW, akked imazanen iW"
  18,107,"Ma d wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, axxam nnsen d leonanat n Loennet"
  18,108,"Degs ad wekkôen, ur ssuturen ayen nniven"
  18,109,"Ini: \"lemmer ill d lmidad, i wawalen n Mass iw, ad iqqaô yill, uqbel ad fukken wawalen n Mass iw, xas a d nawi i t icban n lmidad"
  18,110,"Ini: \"nek d amdan kan, am kunwi. Weêêan iyi d ar Öebbi nnwen, d Öebbi Yiwen. Win issaramen timlilit n Mass is, ad ixdem ayen ilhan, ur ipcarak yiwen deg waâbad n Mass is"
  19,1,Khiâû
  19,2,"Asmekti uêunu n Mass ik, i umdan iS Zakarya"
  19,3,"mi iger, i Mass is, ti$ôi tabavnit"
  19,4,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! S tidep, ôéent laâvam iw, aqeôôu iôeq si ccib. A Mass iw! Anuju $uôeK uroin iyi isnu$ben"
  19,5,"Nek ugade$ llzem iw, deffir i. Tameîîut iw d tiâiqeôt. Efk iyi d lfeôx s$uôeK"
  19,6,"ad iyi iwôet, ad iwôet si twacult n Yaâqub. Err it, a Mass iw, d win iôuvan"
  19,7,"A Zakarya, s tidep, Nbecceô ik s uqcic, ism is Yeêya. Ur Nefki, i yiwen, ism agi, uqbel is"
  19,8,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Amek ara sâu$ aqcic, tameîîut iw d tiâiqeôt, u nek $emqe$ di tewser"
  19,9,"Inna: \"Akka. Inna d Mass ik: ayagi ishel fellI. Ni$ Xelqe$ k, zik, ur telliv d acemma"
  19,10,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Efk iyi d assekni\". Inna: \"assekni ik, ur tepmeslayev i medden, krav wavan, ur tuvnev"
  19,11,"Iffe$ ed ar ugdud is, si lemqam. Iweêêa yasen ad anzen ûûbeê, tameddit"
  19,12,"A Yeêya, eîîef Tazmamt, s loehd\". D ûûebyan, Nefka yas ûûwab"
  19,13,"lmaênana akked ûûfawa, s$uône£. Ipêezzib"
  19,14,ibedd i imawlan is; ur illi d aqehhaô ne$ d amâaûi
  19,15,"Tifrat fellas asmi d ilul, asmi ara immet, asmi ara d iu$al d amuddir"
  19,16,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Meryem, asmi taâzel iman is, si twacult is, di tama ugmuv"
  19,17,"Terra ssteô garas yidsen. Nuzen as d ôôuê nne£. £uôes, amzun d amdan ifuqen"
  19,18,"Tenna: \"ad iyi Ëerz Uênin, segk, ma tepêezzibev"
  19,19,"Inna: \"nek, d amersul kan n Mass im, ad am fke$ aqcic iûfan"
  19,20,"Tenna: \"amek ara sâu$ aqcic, ur iyi innul umdan, ur lli$ d tazennant"
  19,21,"Inna: \"Akka. Inna d Mass im: ayagi, ishel fellI. A t Nerr d assekni i medden, d aêunu s$uône£. D lameô ippuêeppmen"
  19,22,"Tebbwi tadist; syis taâzel iman is, di tama ibaâden"
  19,23,"Bdan p id inzikmiren ar loedra n tezdayt. Tenna: \"anna$ lemmer mmute$, uqbel ayagi, ad pwappu$ akw"
  19,24,"Issawel as d, seddaw as: \"kkes a$wbel, ih, Mass im Irra i$éeô, seddaw am"
  19,25,"Hucc, ar $uôem, loedra n tezdayt, ad am d i$li ppmeô amaynut ibwan"
  19,26,"Eçç, ssew, ssefôeê iéôi m. Ma twalav yiwen n umdan, ini as: nek, s tidep, uéame$ i Uênin, ur pmeslaye$, assa, i umdan"
  19,27,"Tôuê yis ar ugdud is, tebbwi t. Nnan: \"a Meryem! Ni$ tusiv d, s temsalt ihejjnen"
  19,28,"A ultmas n Haôun, ur illi baba m d argaz ucmit, ur telli imma m d tazennant"
  19,29,"Teswâad $uôes. Nnan: \"amek ara nemmeslay i ûûebyan di dduê"
  19,30,"Inna: \"nek d amdan n Öebbi. Ifka yi d Tazmamt. Irra yi d nnbi"
  19,31,"Iôqa yi anda lli$. Iweûûa yi taéallit, u zzakat, skud mazal iyi d amuddir"
  19,32,"Ad bedde$ i yimma. Ur iyi Irri d aqehhaô, ne$ d ccaqi"
  19,33,"Tifrat felli asmi d lule$, asmi ara mmte$, asmi ara d u$ale$ d amuddir"
  19,34,"D wagi ay d Âisa, mmi s n Meryem. D awal n tidep, i$ef cukken"
  19,35,"Ur iûwib ara, i Öebbi, ad Isâu kra n mmi S. Gedha syiS! Ma Iseyya lameô, ad as Yini kan: \"ili\"! Ad yili"
  19,36,"Öebbi, s tidep, d Mass iw, d Mass nnwen. Ihi, âabdet eP. D wagi ay d abrid uwqim"
  19,37,"Mgarraden ikabaren garasen. A tawa$it n wid ijehlen, mara walin ass abarar"
  19,38,"Ara slen, ara walin, ass ideg ara d asen $uône£! Maca, imednas, assa, di ttelfan s ûûeê"
  19,39,"Nabi ten, $ef ass n ssixîa, mara iûaô lameô. Nitni, di l$eflan, nitni ur uminen"
  19,40,"Ih, d Nekwni, ara Iweôten tamurt akked wayen illan fellas. £uône£ tu$alin nnsen"
  19,41,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Ibôahim. Ih, Neppa, illa d bab n tidep, d nnbi"
  19,42,"Mi inna i baba s: \"a baba! Acimi tâabdev win ur nsell, ur nepwali, ur k ip$itin s wacemma"
  19,43,"Ih, a baba, Nek ippunefk iyi d, si tmusni, ayen ur ak neppunefk. Ihi ddu yidi, a k nhu$ ar ubrid ilhan"
  19,44,A baba! Ur âabbed Cciîan. Ni$ Cciîan illa d amâaûu i Uênin
  19,45,"A baba! Nek, ugade$ a k iwwet uâaqeb n Uênin, a ppiliv d ameddakwel n Cciîan"
  19,46,"Inna d: \"day tugiv keçç, a Ibôahim, iôebbiten iw? Ma ur tfukkev ara, war ccekk, a k ôeome$! Ïixxeô iyi tallit $wezzifen"
  19,47,"Inna: \"ili di tifrat. Ad ssutre$ i Mass iw, ad ak Isemmeê. Neppa, s tidep, Iâuzz iyi"
  19,48,"Ad âazle$ iman iw segwen, akked wayen tepnujum, war Öebbi. Ad naâôe$ Mass iw, ahat, s unuju w, ar Mass iw, ur $webne$ ara"
  19,49,"Mi iaâzel iman is segsen akked wayen âabden, war Öebbi, Nefka yas Isêaq akked Yaâqub. Yal yiwen, Nerra t d nnbi"
  19,50,"Nefka yasen seg uêunu nne£. Nerna yasen ccekôan umâin, lfayeq"
  19,51,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Musa. Ih, neppa, illa d aâeôvi, d amazan, d nnbi"
  19,52,"Nessawel as d, si îîeôf ayeffus n udrar. Nessqeôb it id, ad as Nmel"
  19,53,"Nefka yas, seg uêunu nne£, gma s, Haôun, d nnbi"
  19,54,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Ismaâil. Ih, neppa, illa d win ippaîafen di lemâahda s, d amazan, d nnbi"
  19,55,"Iumeô i twacult is, taéallit, zzakat. Iôuva t Mass is"
  19,56,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Idris. Ih, neppa, illa d bab n tidep, d nnbi"
  19,57,Nessuli t s amkan aâlayen
  19,58,"D wigi i I$at Öebbi, ger lambiyya, ger tarwa n Adem, ger wid i Nebbwi akked Nuê, ger tarwa n Ibôahim, akked Isôail, ger wid Nenha u Nefren. Ma $ôan asen issekniyen n Uênin, ad $lin knan, s imeîîawen"
  19,59,"Lxwelf nnsen d asatu i iooan taéallit, ddan d ccehwiyyat. Ad magren ttelfan"
  19,60,"Kkes ed wid isteôoâen, iumnen, xeddmen ayen ilhan. Wigi, ad kecmen Loennet, ur pwadensen s wacemma"
  19,61,"Leonanat n Âaden i Iwaââed Uênin, i imdanen iS, di tbavnit. Lemâahda S, s tidep, a ppevôu"
  19,62,"Ur sellen, degs, i yir awal, siwa: \"tifrat\"! Dinna, lqut nnsen, ûûbeê, tameddit"
  19,63,"D tagi ay d Loennet, ara Nerr d lweôt, i wid ipêezziben, seg imdanen nne£"
  19,64,"Ur d nepûubbu, siwa ma s lameô n Mass ik. IneS i illan zdat nne$, i illan deffir nne$, akked wayen illan garasen. Mass ik ur Iteppu"
  19,65,"Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Ihi, âabed iT, ili d imezgi deg uâbad iS. Day tesnev win isâan ism iS"
  19,66,"La iqqaô umdan: \"ma mmute$, day a yi d ssuff$en d amuddir"
  19,67,"Day ur icfa ara umdan, ar t id Nxelq, zik, ur illi d acemma"
  19,68,"S Mass ik, ara ten Nefser, nitni akked cwaîen. Sinna, a ten Nerr ad zzin i Loahennama, $ef tgwecrar"
  19,69,"Sinna, a d Nekkes, si yal arbaâ, wid ibe$wven nezzeh, ar Uênin"
  19,70,"Sinna, d Nekwni, war ccekk, i Isnen sennig akw, imenza ar tmeô$iwt"
  19,71,"Akken tellam, a pqeôbem $uôes. Akka, ar Mass ik, d aseyyi imuêeppmen"
  19,72,"Sinna, a Nsellek wid ipêezziben. A Neoo degs, imednas, $ef tgwecrar"
  19,73,"Mara asen $ôen issekniyen iberrzen nne£, qqaôen wid ijehlen i wid iumnen: \"menyif sin irebbuyaâ di temâict akw i lemwansa"
  19,74,"Acêal isuta i Nesqucc, uqbel nnsen, ifen ten tarkunt, ûûifa"
  19,75,"Ini: \"ad Irnu Uênin di laâmeô, i im$eôôqen, alamma walan acu i sen ippuwaââden: d aâaqeb ne$ d imir. Ad éôen anwa illan deg umkan adiran mavi, ay d bu lâaskeô uôhifen mavi"
  19,76,"Ad Irnu Öebbi nnhaya i wid ipwanhan. Ar Mass ik, leûlaê idumen ifen akafi, asisi"
  19,77,"Ma twalav win iugin issekniyen nne£, u inna: \"tarkunt, tarwa ad iyi ppunefkent, war ccekk"
  19,78,"Aâni issen tabavnit, ne$ iu$ lemâahda s$uô Uênin"
  19,79,"Xaîi, a Naru ayen inna. Ad as Nessi$wzef nezzeh aâaqeb"
  19,80,"A Newôet ay d inna, a d ias $uône£, d awêid"
  19,81,"Xtaôen, war Öebbi, iôebbiten ar asen d iawin tazmert"
  19,82,"Xaîi! Ad nekôen aâbad nnsen, ad asen u$alen d ixûimen"
  19,83,"Ur twalav ara, Nuzen ed ccwaîen i ijehliyen, la ten laâjen s ljuô"
  19,84,"Ur pêiri fellasen, la Nessalay kan leêsab nnsen"
  19,85,"Ass ideg ara Nefser wid ipêezziben ar Uênin, d imaâôaven"
  19,86,"a Nenheô ijehliyen, d aqwvaô, ar Loahennama"
  19,87,"Ur sâin ccafuâa, siwa win iu$en lemâahda ar Uênin"
  19,88,"Nnan: \"Isâa Uênin, aqcic"
  19,89,Ni$ tebbwim d abeââuq
  19,90,"Segs, qôib flan igenwan, tcerreg tmurt, grurjen idurar s édiê"
  19,91,"Gren aS mmi S, i Uênin"
  19,92,"Ur iwjib ara, i Uênin, ad Isâu mmi S"
  19,93,"Akken llan di tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ay d iteddun, ar Uênin, s waâbad"
  19,94,"Ih, Iêseb iten, Issen nezzeh amvan nnsen"
  19,95,"Akw a d asen $uôeS, ass n tnekra, yiwen yiwen"
  19,96,"War ccekk, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Iâuzz Uênin"
  19,97,"Nerra t kan d ushil, s tmeslayt ik, iwakken a pbeccôev, syis, wid iêezzben, u a pnedôev agdud iggernenn"
  19,98,"Acêal isuta ay Nesqucc uqbel nnsen! Day a pmagrev yiwen degsen, ne$ a ppeslev i uswecwec nnsen"
  20,1,Ïh
  20,2,Ur ak d Nessader ara Leqwôan iwakken a p$weblev
  20,3,D asmekti kan i win ippagwaden
  20,4,D tarusi s$uô Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan aâlayen
  20,5,Aênin i Iâanncen $ef usgeld
  20,6,"IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, i illan garasen, i illan seddaw tmurt"
  20,7,"Ma téaâvev, ihi, Neppa Iéôa sser, akked wayen iffren sennig es"
  20,8,"Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. IneS ismawen imxulaf"
  20,9,Ma tusa k id teqûiî n Musa
  20,10,"Mi iwala times, inna i twacult is: \"qqimet dagi, nek wala$ times. Amar awen d awi$, segs, asafu, ne$ ad afe$, di tmes, nnhaya"
  20,11,"Mi ibbwev $uôes, Ssawlen as d: \"a Musa"
  20,12,"Nek, s tidep, d Mass ik. Ekkes arkasen ik, ih, aql ak di Ïuwa, ta$zut iôqan"
  20,13,"Nek Smenyafe$ k, sell ed i uweêêi"
  20,14,"Nek, s tidep, d Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Nek. Ihi, âabed iyI, ééal ilmend usmekti W"
  20,15,"Imir, s tidep, a d ias. B$i$ a t Ffre$, iwakken yal yiwen a t Nkafi $ef wayen ixdem"
  20,16,"£uôek a k issefôe$ fellas, win ur numin ara yis, i iddan d lhawiyya s! Mulac a pnegrev"
  20,17,"D acu p tinna deg ufus ayeffus ik, a Musa"
  20,18,"Inna: \"d taâkwazt iw, fellas tekkaye$, syis sse$laye$ d iferrawen i lmal iw. Sseqdace$ p i wayen nniven"
  20,19,"Inna: \"veggeô ip, a Musa"
  20,20,"Iveggeô ip, tu$al d azrem, ippeênunuf"
  20,21,"Inna: \"ddem ip, ur ppagwad, ad as Nerr udem is amenzu"
  20,22,"Eémev afus ik, s idis ik. A d iffe$ d amellal, ur ihlik. D assekni nniven"
  20,23,"iwakken ad ak Nessken, seg issekniyen nne£ imeqwôaêanen"
  20,24,"Öuê ar Ferâun. Neppa, s tidep, d aqehhaô"
  20,25,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Lli idmaren iw"
  20,26,Sehhel iyi lameô iw
  20,27,Efsi tiyersi seg iles iw
  20,28,ad fehmen awal iw
  20,29,Efk iyi amâiwen di twacult iw
  20,30,gma Haôun
  20,31,"Ssem$weô, syis, tazmert iw"
  20,32,Zdukkel it ar lameô iw
  20,33,iwakken a K nesbuccaâ aîas
  20,34,a K id nesmekti aîas
  20,35,"Keçç, s tidep, la $ d Tepwaliv"
  20,36,"Inna: \"tepwaqbel tuppra k, a Musa"
  20,37,"Ni$ Nâateq ik, tikelt nniven"
  20,38,"mi Nweêêa, i yimma k, ayen i Nweêêa"
  20,39,"err it deg usenduq, veggeô it s asif. A t issers wasif deg uqeôqaô, a t iddem ucengu W, u d acengu is. Fki$ ak si lmaênana W, a ppeppuôebbiv zdat wallen iW"
  20,40,"Mi telêa ultma k, tenna: \"ma ad awen mle$ w ara itkelfen fellas\"? Nerra k id i yimma k, ad fukken imeîîawen is, ur têezzen ara. Ten$iv amdan, Nsellek ik si le$wben. Njeôôeb ik s lfetnat. Tzed$ev kra iseggwasen ar at Madian. Sinna, tusiv d s lqwedôa, a Musa"
  20,41,Smenyafe$ k i iman iW
  20,42,"Öuêet, keçç akked gma k, s issekniyen iW, ur stehzayet $ef usmekti W"
  20,43,"Öuêet ar Ferâun. Neppa, s tidep, d aqehhaô"
  20,44,"Mmeslayet as s wawal amelêan, amar a d immekti, ne$ ad iagwad"
  20,45,"Nnan: \"a Mass nne$! Nugad ad a$ iglez, ne$ ad ijuô"
  20,46,"Inna: \"ur ppagwadet, Nek, war ccekk, yidwen, Selle$, Pwali"
  20,47,"Öuêet $uôes, tinem as: \"nekwni d imazanen n Mass ik, seddu yidne$ At Isôail, ur ten ppâaqab ara. Aql a$ nusa k id s issekniyen n Mass ik. Tifrat i wi iddan d nnhaya"
  20,48,"S tidep, neppuweêêa d, ar ad ippuâaqeb win inekôen, iwexxôen"
  20,49,"Inna: \"anwa T Mass nnwen, a Musa"
  20,50,"Inna: \"Mass nne$ d Win Ifkan lxelq is i yal cci, sinna, Inha"
  20,51,"Inna: \"amek tevôa d isuta timezwura"
  20,52,"Inna: \"i ten Iéôan, d Mass iw, di Tezmamt. Mass iw ur I$ellev, ur Iteppu"
  20,53,Win i wen irran tamurt d dduê. Iga yawen degs iberdan. Issers ed aman seg igenni. Nessuffu$ ed yissen tiyugiwin n yal ûûenf n le$ôus
  20,54,"Eççet, ekset lmal nnwen. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i imawlan n ddehn"
  20,55,"Segs, Nxelq ikwen; degs, a kwen Nerr; segs, a kwen id Nessuffe$, tikelt nniven"
  20,56,"Ni$ Nessken as akw issekniyen nne£ inkeô, iugi"
  20,57,"Inna: \"day a$ d tusiv, s ssêur ik, a Musa, ad a$ tessuff$ev seg wakal nne"
  20,58,"War ccekk, ad ak d nawi ssêur i t icban. Err garane$ yidek ppaâud, deg umekkan iwulmen, ur t nezgal, ur t tezgalev"
  20,59,"Inna: \"ppaâud nnwen ass n tme$ôa, a d mlilen medden, di tûebêit"
  20,60,"Izzi Ferâun, ijmaâ ed ccbukat is, d$a iusa d"
  20,61,"Inna yasen Musa:\"a tawa$it nnwen! Ur d garet tikerkas $ef Öebbi, a kwen Isxev s uâaqeb. Ni$ ad ixseô win d igren"
  20,62,"Mcawaôen f lameô nnsen, ffren ayen mmeslayen"
  20,63,"Nnan: \"ihi, sin agi d iseêêaren, b$an a kwen ssuff$en seg wakal nnwen, s ssêur nnsen. Ad kksen abrid nnwen amxallef"
  20,64,"Jemâat ed ccbukat nnwen, sinna aset ed d leûfuf. Ni$ ad irbeê, assa, win iufraren"
  20,65,"Nnan: \"a Musa! A pveggôev keçç, ne$ d nekwni ara iveggôen d imezwura"
  20,66,"Inna: \"xaîi, veggôet\"! Si ssêur nnsen, iwala amzun leêêun imraren akked tâakwzin nnsen"
  20,67,"Musa, deg iman is, iêus i lxuf"
  20,68,"Nenna: \"ur ppagwad! Keçç, s tidep, sennig sen"
  20,69,"Veggeô i illan deg ufus ik ayeffus! Ad isseblaâ ay d snulfan\". Ay d snulfan, siwa ccbukat iseêêaren. Anda idda useêêar, ur irebbeê ara"
  20,70,"£¨lin iseêêaren, knan, nnan: \"numen s Mass n Haôun akked Musa"
  20,71,"Inna: \"day tumnem yiS, uqbel i wen serrêe$? Neppa, zi$, d ameqwôan nnwen. Isêefv awen ssêur. War ccekk, ad awen gezme$, avaô sya, afus sya, u a kwen ûemmôe$ af umidag n leodar n tezdayin. A ppeéôem, s tidep, anwa ay d bab uâaqeb meqqwôen, u ara idumen sennig wiyav"
  20,72,"Nnan: \"ur k nesmenyaf, d awez$i, i wayen i $ d iusan ubeggen, akw i Win i $ Ixelqen. Seyyi i k ihwan a pseyyiv. Aseyyi k, d aseyyi $ef tmeddurt n ddunit agi kan"
  20,73,"Ih, numen s Mass nne$, iwakken ad a$ Isemmeê tuccva nne$, akked wayen n ssêur i têeppmev fellane$. Pifxiô Öebbi d Imezgi"
  20,74,"Ih, Loahennama i win iusan ar Mass is, d abe$wvi. Ur ipmeppat degs, ur d ippidir"
  20,75,"Win i iusan $uôeS d lmumen u ixdem ayen ilhan, widak ad ilin deg imukan aâlayen mavi"
  20,76,"leonanat n Âaden, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen din. Ayagi, d akafi i win zeddigen"
  20,77,"Ni$ Nweêêa i Musa: \"ôuê, deg iv, akked imdanen iW. Egg asen abrid akiwan, di yill. Ur ppagwad a kwen in vefôen, ur ppiwêic"
  20,78,"Ferâun, s iâsekôiwen is, vefôen ten. Isseblaâ ten yill, içça ten"
  20,79,"Itlef Ferâun agdud is, ur inhi"
  20,80,"A yAt Isôail! Ni$ Nsellek ikwen seg ucangu nnwen. Nefka yawen ppaâud, ar loiha tayeffus n udrar. Nessers awen d lmenna, ifeôôuoen"
  20,81,"Eççet si lmakla ilhan, i s ikwen N$at. Ur zegret tilas fellas, mulac a kwen immager urrif iW. Win immuger urrif iW, ni$ igrareb"
  20,82,"U Nek, s tidep, Psemmiêe$ i win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d$a ipwanha"
  20,83,"Acu i k i$eûben seg ugdud ik, a Musa"
  20,84,"Inna: \"zgan deffir i. £awle$ d $ureK, a Mass iw, iwakken a Pôaviv"
  20,85,"Inna: \"ih, ni$ Njeôôeb agdud ik, deffir ek. Itelf iten Usamiri"
  20,86,"Iu$al ed Musa s agdud is, s zzâaf d wumri. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Day ur awen Ifka ara, Mass nnwen, lemâahda lâali? Day tâaîîel fellawen lemâahda? Ne$ day teb$am a kwen immager urrif n Mass nnwen? Tzeglem ppaâud iw"
  20,87,"Nnan: \"ur nezgil ppaâud ik, s leb$i nne$. Maca, nbubb tiâakkwmin n ôôêuê n ugdud, d$a nveggeô iten. Akken i iveggeô Usamiri"
  20,88,"Issuffe$ asen d aâejmi, d ameslux isrugmuten. Nnan: \"wagi d ôebbi nnwen u d ôebbi n Musa. Ippu"
  20,89,"Day ur walan ara, ur asen d ippara awal, ur izmir a ten ivuôô, ne$ a ten infaâ"
  20,90,"Ni$ Haôun inna yasen, uqbel: \"a yagdud iw! Teppuhewwlem kan, yis. Mass nnwen, s tidep, d Aênin. Ddut yidi, vefôet lameô iw"
  20,91,"Nnan: \"ur tnepfukku akaber is, d awez$i, alamma iu$al ed Musa $uône"
  20,92,"Inna: \"a Haôun! D acu i k iîîfen, mi ten twalav nnetlafen"
  20,93,Day ur teddiv ara yidi? Day tugiv lameô iw
  20,94,"Inna: \"a mmi s n yimma! Ur iyi ppaîîaf si tamart iw, ne$ seg uqeôôu w. Nek, s tideps, ugade$ ad iyi d tiniv: tessemfaôaqev At Isôail, ur tu$ev awal iw"
  20,95,"Inna: \"d acu t leqsed ik a Usamiri"
  20,96,"Inna: \"wala$ ayen ur walan. Ddme$ d tummeét n lateô umazan, veggôe$ p. Akka ay êusse$ deg iman iw"
  20,97,"Inna: \"ôuê ihi, a ppevôu yidek di tmeddurt a ppeqqaôev: ur iyi pnalet! U, s tidep, $uôek ppaâud ik ur tezmirev a t tzeglev. Muqel ôebbi ik, u$uô mazal teqqimev, ard a t nesseô$, a t ssebruzzaâ ar yill, wakali"
  20,98,"Mass nnwen, siwa Öebbi. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Tamusni S tjemmel yal cci"
  20,99,"Akka i k Nêekku, seg isallen n zik. Ni$ Nefka yak d, s$uône£, asmekti"
  20,100,"Win i s iwexxôen, ad iâabbi taâkkwemt, ass n tnekra"
  20,101,"Ad wekkôen dinna. Ay dir ip fellasen ppaâbga, ass n tnekra"
  20,102,"Ass ideg ara d ûuven di lbuq, a d Nefser ibe$wviyen, zgezwen assen"
  20,103,"Ad swecwicen wa i wa: \"mraw kan i teqqimem"
  20,104,"Nekwni, Nif akw akken Nessen, ayen d qqaôen, mi sen inna yiwen umxallef degsen: \"teqqimem kan ibwass"
  20,105,"Steqsayen k $ef idurar. Ini: \"a ten Issebruzzaâ Mass iw, d iwzan"
  20,106,A ten Irr d aza$aô ibuôen
  20,107,"Ur tepwaliv degs i iâawjen, ne$ i izzren"
  20,108,"Assen, ad vefôen aberraê, war zzrug. Ad irs ûûut zdat Uênin, a ppeslev kan i uswecwec"
  20,109,"Assen, ur ten tenfaâ ccafuâa, siwa i win Iooa Uênin, u Iôuva t $ef wawal"
  20,110,"Issen i illan zdat sen, i illan deffir sen. Ur illi sanda ara T issinen"
  20,111,Ad îîinzen wudmawen i Umuddir n lebda. Ara ixesôen d win ibubben ddens
  20,112,"Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan, u neppa iumen, ur ippagwad ddens, ne$ aqhaô"
  20,113,"Akka, Nessers it id, d Leqwôan s taâôabt. Nenewwel ed, degs, aâeggen, amar ad êezben, u a ten id ias usmekti"
  20,114,"D Ameqwôan Öebbi, Agellid, Tidep. Ur pêiri, di t$uôi, uqbel ma ifukk uweêêi s, $uôek. Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ernu yi di tmusni"
  20,115,"Ni$ Nâahed, zik, Adem. Ippu, ur Nufi $uôes laâzem"
  20,116,"Mi Nenna i lmalayek: \"knumt i Adem\", knant, siwa Iblis i iugin"
  20,117,"Nenna: \"a Adem, wagi, s tidep, d acengu k, akked tmeîîut ik. £urwat a kwen id issuffe$, si Loennet, a p$weblem"
  20,118,"Ih, keçç, degs, ur teplaéev, ur tâarruv"
  20,119,"S tidep, keçç, degs, ur tepfadev, ur k iîîuôôu yiîij"
  20,120,"I$wa t Cciîan, inna: \"a Adem, ad ak ssekne$ ttejôa uwekkeô, akw n tgelda n lebda"
  20,121,"Eççan segs, d$a walan iman nnsen âaryan, bdan la tessôen iman nnsen, s iferrawen n Loennet. Adem iaâûa Mass is, idda di le$wlav"
  20,122,"Sinna, Ifren it Mass is, Issuref as, Inha t"
  20,123,"Inna: \"ûûubet segs akw, wa d acengu n wa. Ma tusa kwen id nnhaya, s$uôI, win iddan d nnhaya iW, ur ipputellef, ur i$webbel"
  20,124,"Win iooan asmekti W, tameddurt is d tucmip. Ass n tnekra, a t Nefser d ader$al"
  20,125,"A d yini: \"a Mass iw! Acimi iyi Tfesrev d ader$al, ni$ lli$ pwali"
  20,126,"A d Yini: \"akken i k id iusan ssekniyen nne£, teppuv iten, akken ara tepwappuv, assa"
  20,127,"Akka ay Nepqeîîi win izegren tilas, ur numin s issekniyen n Mass is. U, s tidep, aâaqeb n laxeôt iwâaô kteô, u ad idum kteô"
  20,128,"Day ur ten inha ara wacêal isuta i Nesqucc, uqbel nnsen? La leêêun $ef tnezdu$in nnsen. Deg wayagi, s tidep, d issekniyen i imawlan n ddehn"
  20,129,"Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal, s$uô Mass ik, akked lajel ipwassnen, yili, war ccekk, iûaô uâaqeb"
  20,130,"Ihi, bibb ayen d qqaôen, sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, uqbel ad inqeô yiîij, uqbel ad i$li, deg iv. Anez di levôuf n wass, amar fellak aôavi"
  20,131,"Ur ppara allen ik ar wayen i Nefka i kra n twaculin nnsen. D ajeooig n tmeddurt di ddunit, iwakken a ten Njeôôeb yis. A$iti n Mass ik yif it, u ad idum kteô"
  20,132,"Ameô taéallit i twacult ik, êerz ip. Ur ak Nessutur ôôeéq, d Nekwni ara k Iôeéqen. Laâquba d aêezzeb"
  20,133,"Nnan: \"a lemmer i $ d iusi s ussekni s$uô Mass is\"! Day ur ten id iusa ara ubeggen, deg wayen illan di tewôeqtin timezwura"
  20,134,"Lemmer iten Nesqucc s uqeîîi, uqbel neppa, a d inin, war ccekk: \"a Mass nne$! Acimi ur a$ d Tunzev ara amazan? A neddu d issekniyen iK, uqbel a nendell u a neppuqeîîi"
  20,135,"Ini: \"akw, la nepgani. Ihi gganit. A ppissinem anwi i iddan d ubrid ilhan, anwi i ipwanhan"
  21,1,"Iqeôb ed i medden uqeîîi nnsen, u nitni stehzan, ur d rzin"
  21,2,"Ur ten d ippas usmekti amaynut, s$uô Mass nnsen, mebla ma ppuraren, mara s sslen"
  21,3,"Ur d rzin wulawen nnsen. Ppemcawaôen wid idensen, s tuffra: \"d acu t wagi, siwa amdan am kunwi? Day a pvefôem ssêur, kunwi tepwalim"
  21,4,"Inna: \"Mass iw Iéôa timenna deg igenni, di tmurt. Neppa Issel, Issen"
  21,5,"Maca, nnan: \"d taffa n tirga. Xaîi! Isnulfa t id. Xaîi! Neppa d amedyaz. Aha san, ad a$ d iawi assekni, akken id ippuceggaâ i imezwura"
  21,6,"Ur tumin, uqbel nnsen, yal temdint Nesqucc, day ad amnen nitni"
  21,7,"Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, siwa irgazen, iwumi Nweêêa. Steqsit imawlan usmekti, ma ur teéôim"
  21,8,Ur ten Nerri d tifekkiwin ur ntepp lqut. Ur wekkôen
  21,9,"Sinna, Neîîef deg wayen i sen Nâahed, u Nsellek iten akked wid i £ ihwan. Nen$a imcumen"
  21,10,"Ih, Nessers awen ed Tazmamt, degs asmekti nnwen. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  21,11,"Acêal n temdinin idensen ay Neôéa! Nexleq, deffir sent, agdud nniven"
  21,12,"Mi êussen i lwaâôan nne£, atnan la regwlen, segs"
  21,13,"Ur regwlet ara, u$alet ar wayen is testasrem, ar ixxamen nnwen. Amar fellawen asteqsi"
  21,14,"Nnan: \"a yamxix nne$, nella, s tidep, d imednas"
  21,15,"Ur tfukk ti$ôi yagi nnsen, armi ten Nerra d aqecqac urhif"
  21,16,"Ur Nexliq ara, i wurar nne£, igenni, tamurt, akked wayen illan garasen"
  21,17,"Lemmer day Neb$i lhawiyya, yili Nebbwi p id, s $uône£, maday Naâna"
  21,18,"Xaîi! Nekkat tikerkas s tidep. Tneqq itent. Neqvent. A tawa$it nnwen, ilmend n wayen d teggarem"
  21,19,"IneS kra illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Wid illan $uôeS, ur sme$wôen ara iman nnsen, $ef uâabed iS. Ur âaggun"
  21,20,"Ppanzen iv akked wass, ur sêissifen"
  21,21,"Ne$ ddmen d, si tmurt, iôebbiten id ipparan ar ddunit"
  21,22,"Lemmer llin degsen iôebbiten, war Öebbi, war ccekk, ad fesden. Gedha s Öebbi, Mass n usgeld, seg wayen id ggaren"
  21,23,"Ur fellaS asteqsi $ef wayen Ixeddem. Nitni, fellasen asteqsi"
  21,24,"Ne$ day ddmen iôebbiten, war Neppa? Ini: \"Awit ed atebbet nnwen\". Ayagi d asmekti i wid illan yidi, d asmekti i wid illan, uqbel i. Maca, tegwti segsen, ur ssinen tidep. D$a zzin akin"
  21,25,"Ur d Nuzen amazan, uqbel ik, siwa ma Nweêêa yas ar: \"ur illi ôebbi siwa Nek, ihi âabdet iyI"
  21,26,"Nnan: \"Isâa Uênin aqcic\". Gedha s yiS! Xaîi! D imdanen imaâzuzen"
  21,27,"Ur S d zeggwiren deg wawal, xedmen s lameô iS"
  21,28,"Iéôa i illan zdat sen, akked wayen illan deffir sen. Ur ççafâan, siwa $ef win Iôuva. U nitni, si lxuf iS, pêadaren"
  21,29,"Win, segsen, id innan: \"nek d ôebbi, war Neppa\", a t Nqeîîi s Loahennama. Akka ay Nepqeîîi imednas"
  21,30,"Ne$ wid ijehlen ur walan ara tamurt akked igenwan llan mlalen? Nessemfaôaq iten, Nga s waman kra n wayen idren. Ihi, day ur ppamnen ara"
  21,31,"Nerra di tmurt idurar, iwakken ur tepêerrik ara yissen. Nerra, degsen, tiza d iberdan, amar ad pwanhun"
  21,32,"Nerra igenni d ssqef innestaôen, u nitni ooan issekniyen nne£"
  21,33,"D Neppa i Ixelqen iv akked wass, iîij akked waggur, yal wa iteddu deg ubrid is"
  21,34,"Ur Nefka ara, uqbel ik, tameddurt n lebda i umdan. Day keçç a ppemmtev, nitni ad wekkôen"
  21,35,"Yal amdan ad ijeôôeb tameppant. Nepjeôôib ikwen s cceôô, akked lxiô. D ahewwel. £uône£ tu$alin nnwen"
  21,36,"Mara k id walin wid ijehlen, pmmaâliken kan fellak: \"d wagi id ikkaten deg iôebbiten nnwen\"? Nitni nekôen asmekti n Uênin"
  21,37,"Ipwaxleq umdan si leêmeq. Ad awen d Ssenâate$ issekniyen iW, ihi, ur iyI $eûbet"
  21,38,"Qqaren: \"melmi lemâahda yagi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  21,39,"Wid ijehlen, a lemmer ad éôen tagwnip ideg ur d tekksen udmawen nnsen, ne$ iârar nnsen, si tmes! Nitni ur pwasellken"
  21,40,"Xaîi! A ten id ias, deqzalla, a ten iwwet ba$a, ur zmiren a t rren, ne$ ad gganin"
  21,41,"Ni$ ttahan $ef imazanen, uqbel ik! Ayen i$ef mmaâlken, izzi d $ef wid, segsen, i ittahan"
  21,42,"Ini: \"anwa ara kwen ifukken, iv akked wass, seg Uênin\"? Maca, ooan asmekti n Mass nnsen"
  21,43,"Ne$ sâan iôebbiten ara ten ifukken, war Nekwni? Ur zmiren ad sellken iman nnsen, ur sâin imâiwnen mgal a£"
  21,44,"Xaîi! Nestaser i wigi akked imezwura nnsen, ar tewser nnsen. Day ur walan ara, Neppas ed ar tmurt, Nessenqas si leryaf is? Day d Nitni ara irebêen"
  21,45,"Ini: \"la kwen nedôe$ kan, s uweêêi\". Ur sellen iâééugen i unabi ma ppunedôen"
  21,46,"Ma iêuza ten uûuvu uâaqeb n Mass ik, war ccekk, a d inin: \"a ssexv nne$! Ih, nella d imednas"
  21,47,"A n Nessers lmizanat iûewben, ass n tnekra. Ur ipwadnes umdan s wacemma. Xas d aâqqa ucceryad, a t id Nawi. Nesteqnaâ yisne£ i uqeîîi"
  21,48,"Ni$ Nefka i Musa akked Haôun, afraz, akked tafat d usmekti, i wid ipêezziben"
  21,49,"Wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, ur T walan, u pêaraben $ef yimir"
  21,50,"Wagi d asmekti iôqan, id Nessader. Day a t tagwim kunwi"
  21,51,"Ni$ Nefka, zik, nnhaya s i Ibôahim? Nella Nessen it"
  21,52,"Mi inna i baba s akked ugdud is: \"d acu tent tâancurin agi, i la tepkabarem"
  21,53,"Nnan d: \"Nufa d imezwura nne$ la tent âabden"
  21,54,"Inna: \"ihi, tellam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen, di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  21,55,"Nnan: \"tusiv a$ d, s tidep, ne$ keçç seg wid ippuraren"
  21,56,"Inna: \"xaîi. Mass nnwen d Mass n tmurt akked igenwan, id Ixleq. Nek, seg inagan n waya"
  21,57,"S Öebbi, ard ad andi$ i tâancuôin nnwen, mara teîîixxôem"
  21,58,"Isseftutes itent, siwa tameqwôant degsent, amar a d u$alen $uôes"
  21,59,"Nnan: \"anwa i igan akka i iôebbiten nne$? Neppa, war ccekk, d amednus"
  21,60,"Nnan: \"nesla i ileméi, itent id iudren, isem is Ibôahim"
  21,61,"Nnan: \"awit ep id, zdat wallen n medden, amar ad ilin d inagan"
  21,62,"Nnan: \"day d keçç i igan akka, i iôebbiten nne$, a Ibôahim"
  21,63,"Inna: \"xaîi, i igan akka, d ameqwôan nnsen agi. Steqsit pen, ma pmeslayen"
  21,64,"Endekwalen d. Nnan: \"ih, d kunwi ay d imednas"
  21,65,"Sinna, bran i iqweôôa nnsen: \"ni$ wigi, teéôiv, ur pmeslayen ara"
  21,66,"Inna: \"day tâabdem, war Öebbi, ayen ur kwen inefâan, ur kwen iîîuôôun, s wacemma"
  21,67,"Tfuh i kunwi, akked wayen tâabdem, war Öebbi! Day ur tefhimem ara"
  21,68,"Nnan: \"sseô$et ep, u sellket iôebbiten nnwen, ma tâazmem"
  21,69,"Nenna: \"a times, ili d tasmuvi u d talwit, i Ibôahim"
  21,70,Undin as p. Nerra ten d imexsuôen mavi
  21,71,"Nsellek it, akked Luî, ar tmurt i Neôqa i imavalen"
  21,72,"Nefka yas Isêaq, Nerna yas Yaâqub. I sin, Nerra ten d wid imaânen"
  21,73,"Nerra ten d imvebbôen, nehhun s lameô nne£. Nweêêa yasen igiten ilhan, taéallit, azekki. Llan d wid i £ iâabden"
  21,74,"I Lut, Nefka ûûwab, tamusni. Nsellek it si temdint i illan txeddem tucmitin. Llan, s tidep, d agdud n dir, d laâôuô"
  21,75,"Nesskecm it deg uêunu nne£. Neppa, ih, seg wid imaânen"
  21,76,"I Nuê, zik, mi inâaô. Njaweb as ed. Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, si lefqaâ abarar"
  21,77,"Neneêêel it mgal agdud i iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Llan, s tidep, d agdud n dir. Ne$ves iten meôôa"
  21,78,"I Dawed akked Sliman, mi êudden $ef yiger, ideg ksant wulli n medden. Nella d Inagan uêuddu nnsen"
  21,79,"Nessfehm as p i Sliman. I sin, Nefka ûûwab, tamusni. Nêeppem i idurar akked igvav ad sbuccâen Dawed. D ayen Newqem"
  21,80,"Nessêefv as, ad awen iûnaâ iceîîiven, ara iêarben fellawen si tiytiwin. Day a ppesnemmrem"
  21,81,"I Sliman, avu n tarikt, ipûuvu s lameô is, $er tmurt i Neôqa. Nezga Néeô yal cci"
  21,82,"Ger ccwaîen, wa i$evves as, wa iqubel cce$l nniven. Nella d imêaraben nnsen"
  21,83,"I Yub, mi inuj $eô Mass is: \"nek pwa$e$. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun"
  21,84,"Njaweb as ed. Nekkes as it ivuôôen; Nerra yas d tawacult is, akw, yides, tin i p icban. D aêunu s$uône£, d asmekti i iâabaden"
  21,85,"Ismaâil, Idris, Dulkifl, akken ma llan, d iûebôiyen"
  21,86,"Nesskecm iten deg uêunu nne£. Nitni, s tidep, seg wid imaânen"
  21,87,"I Dannun, mi iôuê s wurrif. I$il ur Nesâi ara adabu fellas. Inâaô, di tellis: \"ur illi ôebbi siwa Keçç. Gedha s yiseK! Nek lli$ si imednas"
  21,88,Njaweb as ed. Nâateq it si éémik. Akka ay Nâateq lmumnin
  21,89,"I Zakaria, mi inuj $uô Mass is: \"a Mass iw! Ur iyi Ippaooa ara d amengur. Keçç, Tifev akw iweôôaten"
  21,90,"Njaweb as ed. Nefka yas Yaêia, Nesseêla yas tameîîut is. Nitni, s tidep, izga izwar lxiô nnsen. Pnujun $uône£, s tugwdi d usirem. Unzen a£"
  21,91,"Ar tin i iqqimen zeddiget, Nûuv si ôôuê nne£. Nerra p, neppat akked mmi s, d assekni i imavalen"
  21,92,"Lois agi nnwen, war ccek, d lois yiwen. Nek d Mass nnwen, ihi âabdet iyI"
  21,93,"Gezmen lameô nnsen garasen. £uône£, akw, ara d u$alen"
  21,94,"Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan u irna iumen, ur ipôuêu laâtab is. Ih, Nekwni Nepparu fellas"
  21,95,Ipwagdel asen a d u$alen $eô temdint i Nesqucc
  21,96,"alamma serrêen d i Iaouo d Maouo. Nitni, si yal ti$ilt, a d azzlen"
  21,97,"Tqeôb ed lemâahda n tidep. Atan iqquô yiéôi n wid ijehlen: \"a tawa$it nne$! Ni$ nella ne$fel $ef waya. U, aâer, nella d imednas"
  21,98,"Kunwi, s tidep, akked wayen tâabden, war Öebbi, d is$aôen n Loahennama. £ures, kunwi, teppeddum"
  21,99,"Lemmer llin widak d iôebbiten, ur p keççmen. Akw, ad wekkôen degs"
  21,100,"I nitni, degs, zzhir. Nitni, degs, ur sellen"
  21,101,"Ma d wid iwumi izwar ssaâd, s$uône£, widak, segs, ad baâden"
  21,102,Ur sellen i ûûut is. Ad wekkôen deg wayen cihwant teôwiêin nnsen
  21,103,"Ur ten i$webbel lweêc abarar. A ten magrent lmalayek: \"assa, d ass nnwen, i wen ippuwaââden"
  21,104,"Ass ideg ara Nesnefvas igenni am tweôqep n tira, akken Nebda axlaq amezwaru, ad as Nales. D lemâahda fellane£. Akka, ih, ara Nexdem"
  21,105,"Ni$ Nura deg Ihellilen, deffir usmekti: \"ara iweôten tamurt, d imdanen iW imaânen"
  21,106,"Deg wayagi, war ccekk, d asali i ugdud iâabbaden"
  21,107,"Ur k id Nuzen, siwa d aêunu i imavalen"
  21,108,"Ini: \"iyi d ippuweêêan, siwa: Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen kan. Kunwi ma d imvuâen"
  21,109,"Ma wexxôen, ini: \"âaggne$ awen, akken ma tellam; ur éôi$ ma iqôeb, ne$ ibâad, ayen i wen ippuwaââden"
  21,110,"Neppa, s tidep, Issen awal d iff$en, Issen ayen tessusmem"
  21,111,"Ur éôi$ ma, ayagi, ahat d ahewwel nnwen, u d zzhu n tallit kan"
  21,112,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Eêkem s tidep. Mass nne$, Aênin, i nepper d Amâiwen, mgal ayen teppandim"
  22,1,"A yimdanen! Ëezzbet i Mass nnwen, zzenzla n yimir, stidep, d tadyant tabarart"
  22,2,"Ass ideg ara p twalim, yal timôebbit a ppeppu win tessuîîuv, yal tadist a ppexseô. A pwaliv imdanen ssekôen, ur sskiôen. Maca, aâaqeb n Öebbi iwâaô"
  22,3,"Ger yimdanen, illa win ipnamaren $ef Öebbi, war tamusni. Iteddu d yal cciîan imcebbwel"
  22,4,"Iura fellas: \"ar wagi, win i t irran d bab is, ara t itlef, s tidep, u a t inheô ar uâaqeb ujajiê"
  22,5,"A yimdanen! Ma di ccekk ay tellam f tnekra, ihi, Nekwni, s tidep, Nxelq ikwen seg wakal, sinna, si tiqqit n l$ella, sinna, seg urgan, sinna, si tecriêt, texleq ur texliq, iwakken ad awen Nbeggen. Neppara, di tâabbuvin, ayen i £ ihwan, alamma d lajel ipwassnen. Sinna, Nessuffu$ ikwen id d llufanat, sinna a ppim$uôem. Segwen llan wid ippemmten, u segwen win ara iawven d awessur, ard ur ippisin acemma seg wayen issen. A pwalid akal d a$uôaô. Ma Nesse$li d ageffur fellas, ad ikker, ad icuff, a d ifk tayuga n yal ûûenf uziyn n le$ôus"
  22,6,"Ayagi, acku Öebbi d Tidep. D Neppa id Issidiren lmeggtin. Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  22,7,"U imir a d ias, war ccekk fellas. U Öebbi a d Issker wid illan di tneîlin"
  22,8,"Ger imdanen, illa win ipnamaren $ef Öebbi, war tamusni, ne$ nnhaya, ne$ Tazmamt ifeten"
  22,9,"Icuff aqenduô, iwakken ad itlef seg ubrid n Öebbi. Fellas xezzu di ddunit. Deg wass n tnekra, a Nessuk fellas aâaqeb n tmeô$iwt"
  22,10,"Ayagi, $ef wayen id urwen ifassen ik. U Öebbi ur Idennis imdanen"
  22,11,"Ger yimdanen, win iâabden Öebbi, $ef rrif. Ma iusa t id lxiô, ad ithenni yis. Ma iusa t id uhewwel, ad iswexxeô udem is. Öuêent as, ddunit, laxeôt. Ayagi d lexsaôa n ûûeê"
  22,12,"Ipnuju, war Öebbi, ar wayen ur t neîîuôôu, ur t neffaâ. D wagi ay d ttelfan u$miq"
  22,13,"Ipnuju ar bu vveôô izwaren aba$uô ines. Ay d bab ucmit, ay d acrik ucmit"
  22,14,"Öebbi, s tidep, ad Issekcem wid iumnen, i ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar Loennet, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen. Öebbi, s tidep, Ixeddem ayen Ib$a"
  22,15,"Win i oaâlen ur t Ipsellik ara Öebbi, di ddunit, di laxeôt, ad iâalleq amrar s igenni, sinna, ad igzem nnefs is. Ad iéeô ma tiêêeôci s temêa ayen i t irêan"
  22,16,"Akka ay t id Nessader, d issekniyen iberrzen. U Öebbi, s tidep, Inehhu win i S ihwan"
  22,17,"Ih, ass n tnekra, ad Iêudd Öebbi ger wid iumnen, udayen, iûabiyen, imasiêiyen, u iâabbaden n tmes, wid ipcaraken. Öebbi, s tidep, Iwala yal cci"
  22,18,"Ur twalav ara knan i Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt: iîij, aggur, itran, idurar, ttjuô, lêayawan, aîas n yimdanen. Aâaqeb d lewoeb $ef aîas. Win Isdull Öebbi, ur illi w ara t iâuzzen. Ih, Öebbi Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan"
  22,19,"Atnan sin ixûimen ppemqellaân $ef Mass nnsen. S tmes ay pwafeûlen iceîîiven n wid ijehlen. Ad mmiren, $ef iqweôôa nnsen, waman iô$an"
  22,20,"ara issefsin ayen illan deg iâabbav nnsen, akked igwelman"
  22,21,"I nitni, ijekwaven n wuzzal"
  22,22,"Yal tikelt ara ssirmen a d ff$en segs, seg wakken meênen, a ten rren $uôes: \"jeôôbet aâaqeb n tmeô$iwt"
  22,23,"Öebbi, s tidep, ad Issekcem wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar Loennet, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen. Degs ad qqnen imeqyasen n ddheb d lyaqut. Leêrir deg iceîîiven nnsen"
  22,24,"Pwanhan s awal umâin, pwanhan s abrid Umaâzuz"
  22,25,"Ih, i wid ijehlen i issefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, akked Loamaâ n Lêaôam, i Nerra i imdanen, ama d amezda$ n din, ama d abeôôani; i win ib$an degs tijehli, s ddens, a Nesâaddi aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  22,26,"Mi Nhegga i Ibôahim, amkan n Uxxam: \"ur iyI pcarak acemma! Zizdeg axxam iW i wid idewwiôen, wid ibedden, wid iîîinizen, iknan"
  22,27,"Enced medden ar lêio. A d asen $uôek $ef uvaô, ne$ $ef yal amerkub ulîif. A d asen si yal abrid ibaâden"
  22,28,"Ad cehhden $ef l$it nnsen. A d smektin ism n Öebbi, deg ussan ipwassnen, $ef ubhim n lmal i sen Ifka. Eççet segs, cceççet ame$bun, aéawali"
  22,29,"Sinna, ad ssirden, ad qenâen asirem nnsen, ad dewwôen i Uxxam aqdim"
  22,30,"Akka. Win ippâuzzun ayen Igdel Öebbi, ilha yas kteô, ar Mass is. Ëellen awen lmal, siwa wid i wen mlan. Janbet lâaô n tâancuôin, janbet awal n ééuô"
  22,31,"am wid imalen ar tidep ar Öebbi, ur aS pcaraken. Win ipcaraken i Öebbi, amzun i$li d seg igenni, u iccelqef it ufôux, ne$ inheô it wavu, s amekkan lqayen"
  22,32,"Akka. Win ippâuzzun isekkiren n Öebbi, ihi, d aêezzeb n wulawen"
  22,33,"I kunwi degs aba$uô ar lajel ipwassnen, sinna, îêegga nnsen ar Uxxam aqdim"
  22,34,"I yal lois, Nefka asekkir, iwakken a d smektin ism n Öebbi, $ef ubhim n lmal is iten N$at. Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen. Ihi, anzet aS. Becceô itubiyen"
  22,35,"wid iwumi ppergigin wulawen nnsen mara d mmektin Öebbi, wid iûebbôen i wayen iten iu$en, wid ipéallan u pseddiqen seg wayen is iten N$at"
  22,36,"Lmal iqebbwan, Nerra yawen ten, seg isekkiren n Öebbi. Degsen lfayda i kunwi. Bedret fellasen isem n Öebbi, mara d rsen. Mi $lin $ef ibeôdiyen nnsen, eççet segsen, cceççet aâîîaô, aéawali. Akka ay d Nenub fellawen yissen, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  22,37,"Ur ippawev ar Öebbi uksum nnsen, ne$ idamen nnsen, d awez$i. Ara T iawven, d aêezzeb nnwen. Am akka, Inub fellawen yissen, iwakken ad aS tgem ccan i Öebbi, ilmend n nnhaya nnwen s$uôeS. Becceô wid imaânen"
  22,38,"Ih, Öebbi Ipfukku wid iumnen. Ih, Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara yal lxayen ajehli"
  22,39,"Tsriê i wid ipwawwven imi pwadensen - Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer a ten Isellek"
  22,40,"wid id ssuff$en seg ixxamen nnsen, war ssebba, imi kan qqaôen: \"Mass nne$ d Öebbi\". Lemmer ur Iswexxiô ara Öebbi imdanen, kra s kra, ara ipwahudden, war ccekk, d tiqwebtin, timezgida, lemûellat, lowamaâ ideg d smektayen, aîas, ism n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ippaâwan win iT ippaâwanen. Öebbi, s tidep, d Uohid, d Uzmir"
  22,41,"Wid, ma Nessqâad iten di tmurt, bedden i téallit, pzekkin, ppamôen lewqama, gedlen tuccva. Ar Öebbi ara d gwrin lumuô"
  22,42,"Ma skaddben k, ni$ skaddben, uqbel nnsen, igduden n Nuê, Âad, akked Tamud"
  22,43,"agdud n Ibôahim, akked ugdud n Luî"
  22,44,"At Madyan. Skaddben Musa. Fki$ lmudda i ijehliyen, sinna, Zzi$ d fellasen. A tuzzma W imiren"
  22,45,"Acêal n temdinin ay Nesqucc imi densent. Haatent ppint. Xlan lebyar, akked lebruo uohiden"
  22,46,"Day ur unagen ara di tmurt? Ad sâun, $ef waya, ulawen ad fehmen yissen, imeééu$en ara islen yissen. Maca, maççi d allen, d ulawen deg idmaren i idre$len"
  22,47,"B$an k a d tesqeôbev aâaqeb. Öebbi ur Ipzeggil lemâahda S, d awez$i. Ni$ ass, ar Mass ik, am agim iseggwasen, s leêsab nnwen"
  22,48,"Acêal n temdinin iwumi Fki$ lmudda, u irna densent. Sinna, Zzi$ fellasent. £uôI tu$alin"
  22,49,"Ini: \"a yimdanen! Nek, $uôwen, d aneddaô kan ipbegginen"
  22,50,"I wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ssmaê akked ôôeéq ukyis"
  22,51,"Wid iaânan asfunneg issekniyen nne£, widak d at ujajiê"
  22,52,"Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, amazan ne$ nnbi, mebla ma ikecm ed Cciîan, deg wayen imenna, ma imenna. Itekkes Öebbi ayen d issekcam Cciîan, sinna, Itebbit issekniyen iS. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  22,53,"Iwakken ad Irr aggway n Cciîan d ahewwel, i at wulawen iblan akked at wulawen aquôan. Ih, imednas atnan di t$ennant tu$miqt"
  22,54,"Iwakken ad éôen wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni, ar neppa d tidep, s$uô Mass ik. Ad amnen yis. Ad as anzen wulawen nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Inehhu wid iumnen, s abrid uwqim"
  22,55,"Zgan wid ijehlen di ccekk fellas, ar ten id ias yimir, deqzalla, ne$ ibbwev iten id uâaqeb n wass abarar"
  22,56,"Assen, tagelda i Öebbi. Ad Iêudd garasen. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad ilin di Loennet n ssuâada"
  22,57,"I wid ijehlen, iskaddben issekniyen nne£, aâaqeb isdullun"
  22,58,"Wid iunagen, deg ubrid n Öebbi, sinna, pwan$an ne$ mmuten, a ten I$it Öebbi, war ccekk, s ôôeéq umâin. Ih, Öebbi Yif akw im$iten"
  22,59,"A ten Issekcem anekcum ara ôadin. Ih, Öebbi d Amusnaw, Iêellem"
  22,60,"Akka. Win iâaqben akken ippuâaqeb, sinna, ipwadnes, war ccekk, a t Isellek Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ipqili, Ipsemmiê"
  22,61,"Akka, acku Öebbi Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. U Öebbi Issel, Ipwali"
  22,62,"Akka, acku Öebbi d tidep, ma d ayen u$uô pnujun, war Neppa, d tikerkas. Ih, Öebbi d Aâlâyan, d Ameqwôan"
  22,63,"Day ur twalav ara Öebbi Isse$li d aman, seg igenni, d$a izzegzew wakal? Ih, Öebbi d Laîif, Iéôa"
  22,64,"IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ih, Öebbi, ar Neppa d Asâay d Amaâzuz"
  22,65,"Ur twalav ara Öebbi Inub ed fellawen s wayen illan di tmurt, akked lbabur ippazalen di yill, s lameô iS. Iîîef igenni ur d i$elli f tmurt, siwa ma Iunef as. Ih, Öebbi, war ccekk, Issuruf u Ipêunu i imdanen"
  22,66,"D Neppa ikwen Issadren, sinna, ara kwen In$en, sinna, ara kwen id Issadren. Amdan, s tidep, d ajehli"
  22,67,"I yal lois, Nefka asekkir, teddun degs. Ulay$eô i k pna$en $ef lameô. Nuj ar Mass ik; ih, aql ak, keçç, di nnhaya tuwqimt"
  22,68,"Ma numren k, ini: \"Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen ayen txeddmem"
  22,69,"Öebbi ad Iêudd garawen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen tellam temgarradem"
  22,70,"Day ur teéôiv ara Öebbi Issen i illan deg igenni akked tmurt? Ayagi, s tidep, di Tezmamt. Ih, ayagi ishel i Öebbi"
  22,71,"La âabden, war Öebbi, ayen iwumi ur d Issers adabu, ayen ur ssinen. Imednas, ur illi wa ara ten isellken"
  22,72,"Ma mlan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, a pâaqlev asmmummi deg udmawen n wid ijehlen. Qôib ad éevmen $ef wid i sen iqqaôen issekniyen nne£. Ini: \"a kwen xebbôe$ af wayen i$elben aya: times i Iâahed Öebbi i wid ijehlen\". A tu$alin tucmip"
  22,73,"A yimdanen! Ippunefk ed umedya, selt as d: ih, wid u$uô tepnujum, war Öebbi, ur zmiren, d awez$i, a d xelqen izi, xas mlalen $ef waya. Ma illa wayen i sen iuker yizi, ur zmiren ad as t id kksen. D uôhif umsuter, d uôhif win issuter"
  22,74,"Ur qudôen ara Öebbi, azal n lqedô iS. Ih, Öebbi d Uohid, d Uzmir"
  22,75,"Öebbi Iferren imazanen ger lmalayek, u ger imdanen. Ih, Öebbi Issel, Ipwali"
  22,76,"Issen i illan zdat sen, i illan deffir sen. Ar Öebbi ad u$alen lumuô"
  22,77,"A wid iumnen! Ïîinzet u knut, âabdet Mass nnwen, xedmet lxiô, amar a prebêem"
  22,78,"Jahdet ar Öebbi lêeqq ujahed iS. Neppa Ifren ikwen. Ur kwen Ihejjen ara di ddin, ddin ubabat wen Ibôahim. Neppa, i wen isemman, zik, imvuâen. Deg waya, ad yili Umazan d anagi nnwen, u a ppilim d inagan n medden. Ihi, ééallet, zekkit, teîîfem di Öebbi. Neppa d Bab nnwen. D Bab amxallef, d Asellak amxallef"
  23,1,Ni$ lmumnin rebêen
  23,2,Wid ipéallan s wannuz
  23,3,wid ijunben yir awal
  23,4,wid ipzekkin
  23,5,wid iêurben af tuzzuft nnsen
  23,6,"siwa ar tlawin nnsen, ne$ taklatin nnsen. Akka, ur degsen tiyta"
  23,7,"wid ib$an sennig waya, widak zegren tilisa"
  23,8,"wid ipqadaren lamanat nnsen, u lemâahda nnsen"
  23,9,wid iwennâen tiéilla nnsen
  23,10,D wigi ay d iweôôaten
  23,11,"wid ara iweôten Loennet, degs ad wekkôen"
  23,12,"Ni$ Nexleq amdan, seg ufûil n talaxt"
  23,13,"sinna, Nerra t d tiqqit deg umekkan n laman"
  23,14,"sinna, tiqqit Nxelq ip d argen; d$a, argen Nxelq it d acelleqluq; d$a, acelleqluq Nxelq it d i$san; d$a, Nessels aksum i yi$san. Sinna, Nxelq it d lxelq amaynut. Ad Ibarek Öebbi, Imxeyyeô ixellaqen"
  23,15,"Sinna, deffir waya, war ccekk, a ppemmtem"
  23,16,"Sinna, ih, ass n tnekra, a d tu$alem"
  23,17,"Ni$ Nexleq, sennig wen, ûa iberdan. Ur Nelli, $ef uxlaq, seg i$wefliyen"
  23,18,"Nessader ed, seg igenni, aman s lmizan. Naâteq iten di tmurt. Nezmer a ten Nessôuê"
  23,19,"Nxelq awen, yissen, leonanat n tezdayin akked téuôin; degsen, i kunwi, aîas n yizwayen, teppeppem segsen"
  23,20,"Akked ttejôa, id iff$en seg udrar n Sina. Teppak ed zzit u ddhin, i wid iteppen"
  23,21,"Ih, di lmal, aselmed i kunwi. Nesswa kwen s wayen illan deg iâabbav nnsen. Aîas n uba$uô degsen, i kunwi. Teppeppem segsen"
  23,22,"Fellasen, u $ef lbabuô, ppawin kwen"
  23,23,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi. Ur awen illi ôebbi, war Neppa. Day ur tepêezziben ara"
  23,24,"Nnan imvebbôen ijehliyen, n ugdud is: \"wagi d amdan kan, am kunwi; ib$a a d ikk sennig wen. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, a d Issers lmalayek. Ur nesli s waya, ar lejdud nne$ imezwura"
  23,25,"Neppa d argaz kan aôehbani. Qaôaâet ep, tallit kan"
  23,26,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Awes iyi, skaddben iyi"
  23,27,"Nweêêa yas d: \"eûnaâ lbabuô, ger wallen nne£, s uweêêi nne£. Mi d iusa lameô nne£, la pfeggiven igwefran, d ihedman, awi degs, tayuga n yal ûûenf, akked twacult ik, siwa wid, segsen, i$ef id izwar wawal. Ur iyI d steqsay af wid idensen, nitni, war ccekk, ad pwa$evsen"
  23,28,"Mi tâanncev di lbabur, keçç akked wid illan yidek, ini: ccekôan i Öebbi i $ Iselken seg ugdud imednas"
  23,29,"Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ssers iyi deg umekkan iôqan; Keçç Tifev akw wid issrusun"
  23,30,"War ccekk, ayagi, d issekniyen, u Nekwni, Nezga d wid ipjeôôiben"
  23,31,"Sinna, Nxelq ed, deffir sen, isuta nniven"
  23,32,"Nuzen asen d amazan, segsen: \"âabdet Öebbi, ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Day ur tepêezzibem ara"
  23,33,"Nnan imvebbôen ijehliyen n ugdud is, wid iugin u inekôen timlilit n laxeôt, wid Ne$na di tmeddurt n ddunit: \"wagi d amdan kan am kunwi, itepp seg wayen teppeppem, itess seg wayen teppessem"
  23,34,"Ma tessemêessem i umdan i kwen icban, war ccekk, kunwi seg imexsuôen"
  23,35,"Day i wen iâahed ard a d teff$em mara temmtem, tu$alem d akal, d i$san"
  23,36,"Ibâad, Ibâad, ayen i wen ippuwaââden"
  23,37,"I illan kan, d tameddurt n ddunit. A nemmet, a nidir, nekwni ur d neppenkar"
  23,38,"Neppa, d argaz kan id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi. Nekwni, ur numin yis"
  23,39,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Awes iyi, skaddben iyi"
  23,40,"Inna: \"garane$ d cwiî, a d gwrin di nndama"
  23,41,"Iwwet iten usu$u, s tidep. Nerra ten d rrmim. Err akin, agdud imednas"
  23,42,"Sinna, Nxelq ed, deffir sen, isuta nniven"
  23,43,"Lois ur d isseqôab, ur iswexxiô, lajel is"
  23,44,"Sinna, Nuzen ed imazanen nne£, wa deffir wa. Yal tikelt ideg ara d ias umazan, ar lois is, a t skiddben. Nerra ten mestebâan, Nerra ten d tidyanin. Err akin, agdud ur neppamen"
  23,45,"Sinna, Nuzen ed Musa akked gma s Haôun, s issekniyen nne£, akked udabu n ûûeê"
  23,46,eô Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Sme$wôen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud amzuxxi
  23,47,"Nnan: \"Day a namen sin imdanen am nekwni, u agdud nnsen d aklan nne"
  23,48,"Skaddben ten, d$a u$alen seg wid ipwan$an"
  23,49,"Ni$ Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, amar ad pwanhun"
  23,50,"Nerra mmi s n Meryem, akked imma s, d assekni. Nesduri ten di ti$ilt, degs laman d waman"
  23,51,"A yimazanen, eççet seg wayen imaânen, xedmet ayen ilhan, Nek, èôi$ ayen txeddmem"
  23,52,"Lois agi nnwen, s tidep, d lois yiwen. Nek, d Mass nnwen, ihi êezbet iyI"
  23,53,"Bvan lameô nnsen garasen, mi mfaôaqen. Yal akabar ifôeê s wayla s"
  23,54,"Eoo iten di maylellif nnsen, tallit kan"
  23,55,"Day $ilen mi sen Nefka ayla, tarwa"
  23,56,"ad asen Nezzazal lxiô? Xaîi, ur faqen"
  23,57,"Ih, wid, si tugwdi n Mass nnsen, pêadaren"
  23,58,wid iumnen s issekniyen n Mass nnsen
  23,59,wid ur nepcarak i Mass nnsen
  23,60,"wid ippaken ayen fkan, ulawen nnsen ugaden mi, nitni, ad u$alen ar Mass nnsen"
  23,61,"widak, pêirin ar lxiô u, $uôes, zeggwiren"
  23,62,"Ur Nepkellif taôwiêt, siwa ar wayen iwumi tezmer. £uône£ Tazmamt, tessawal tidep. Nitni ur twadensen"
  23,63,"Maca, ulawen nnsen di maylellif, $ef tagi. U rnan yir igiten i waya, a ten xedmen"
  23,64,"Alamma, mi Nesâadda aâaqeb $ef isâayen nnsen, a d su$en"
  23,65,"Ur psu$ut, ass agi, kunwi, segne$, ur tepwasellkem"
  23,66,"Ni$ mlan awen issekniyen iW, trewlem asen"
  23,67,"tesme$wôem iman nnwen fellasen. Teppaâwazem, tekkatem"
  23,68,"Day ur meyyzen ara Awal? Day ur ten id iusa ara, wayen ur d nusi ar lejdud nnsen imezwura"
  23,69,"Ne$ day ur ssinen ara amazan nnsen, imi t nekôen"
  23,70,"Ne$ qqaôen: \"ikcem it loenn\"? Xaîi, iusa ten id s tidep. Tegwti degsen, kerhen tidep"
  23,71,"Lemmer tedda tidep d lhawiyyat nnsen, war ccekk, tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan degsen, ad fesden. Xaîi, Nebbwi yasen d asmekti nnsen. Nitni asmekti nnsen ooan t"
  23,72,"Ne$, ad asen tessutrev taqdiât? Ppif taqdiât n Mass ik. Neppa Yif akw iôeééaqen"
  23,73,"Keçç, s tidep, la ten tneccdev s abrid uwqim"
  23,74,"Wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, s tidep, ff$en i ubrid"
  23,75,"Xas Nêun fellasen, u Nekkes asen ccqa nnsen, ad vellelen di leqheô nnsen, ad ddebdeben"
  23,76,"Ni$ Nesâadda fellasen aâaqeb. Ur knan i Mass nnsen, ur nujen"
  23,77,"Armi, mara asen Nelli tabburt uâaqeb iqesêen, imiren, degs, ad aysen"
  23,78,"Neppa i wen Ixelqen timesliwt, iéôi, ulawen. Drus ay tesnemmirem"
  23,79,Neppa ikwen Iwezzâen di tmurt. £uôeS ara tepwafesrem
  23,80,"Neppa i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. IneS afraz n yiv akked wass. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  23,81,Xaîi. Nnan akken d nnan imezwura
  23,82,"Nnan: \"Ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, d i$san, day a $ d ssekren"
  23,83,"Ni$ ippuâahed wayagi i nekwni, akw, zik, i imezwura nne$. Ayagi, siwa d timucuha imezwura"
  23,84,"Ini: \"wi p ilan tmurt, akked wayen illan degs, ma tessnem"
  23,85,"A d inin: \"d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ihi, day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  23,86,"Ini: \"anwa ay d Mass n ûa igenwan? Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan"
  23,87,"A d inin: \"d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ihi, day ur tepêezzibem ara"
  23,88,"Ini: \"anwa i Isâan tagelda n yal cci, ger ifassen iS; Neppa Ipêarab, ur illi uêareb fellaS, ma teppissinem"
  23,89,"A d inin: \"d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ihi, acimi tepwamelkem"
  23,90,"Xaîi! Nefka yasen tidep, nitni, war ccek, d ikeddaben"
  23,91,"Ur Isâi Öebbi mmi S. Ur illi ôebbi ar tama S. Mulac yal ôebbi ad iawi ayen id ixleq, wa ad iagwar wa. Gedha s Öebbi, seg wayen id snulfuyen"
  23,92,"Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. D Aâlayan, sennig wayen pcaraken"
  23,93,"Ini: \"a Mass iw! Lemmer a yi d Tesseknev acu i sen ippuâahden"
  23,94,"A Mass iw, ur iyi Ppara deg ugdud imednas"
  23,95,"S tidep, Nezmer ad ak Nessken acu i sen Nâahed"
  23,96,"Err akin tucmip s lfayeq. Nekwni Neéôa, sennig wiyav, ayen d snulfuyen"
  23,97,"Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ëerz iyi seg u$wayen n ccwaîen. Êë"
  23,98,"Ëerz iyi, a Mass iw! Ur dgi ppilin"
  23,99,"Armi, mi d tusa tmeppant yiwen degsen, inna: \"a Mass iw! Err iyi"
  23,100,"amar ad xedme$ ayen ilhan deg wayen ooi$\". Xaîi, d awal kan id inna. Tella, deffir es, tse$lit, alamma d ass n tnekra"
  23,101,"Ma ûuven di lbuq, assen, ur ppemyilin, ur pmesteqsayen"
  23,102,"Wid iwumi ééay lmizan nnsen, nitni rebêen"
  23,103,"Wid iwumi fessus lmizan nnsen, d nitni i issexsôen iman nnsen. Di Loahennama ad wekkôen"
  23,104,"A ppesser$ tmes udmawen nnsen, ad asen zelgen icenfiren"
  23,105,"Day ur awen qaren ara issekniyen iW, wanag la ten tnekôem"
  23,106,"Nnan: \"a Mass nne$! I$leb ane$ ccum nne$. Nella d agdud im$eôqen"
  23,107,"A Mass nne$! Ssuffe$ ane$ segs. Ma nesnager, ihi, d imednas ay nella"
  23,108,"Ad Yini: \"qqimet degs, ur pmeslayet"
  23,109,"Ih, illa urbaâ n imdanen iW i iqqaôen: \"a Mass nne$! Numen. Semmeê ane$, Ëun fella$, Keçç Tifev akw wid ipêunun"
  23,110,"Tettihim fellasen armi i wen sseppun asmekti W, u tdessem degsen"
  23,111,"Nek, assa, Kufa$ ten $ef wayen ûebôen. D nitni, war ccekk, ay d imerbaê"
  23,112,"Inna: \"acêal iseggwasen i teqqimem deg wakal"
  23,113,"Nnan: \"Neqqim ass, ne$ ur ibbwiv wass, steqsi wid iêepben"
  23,114,"Inna: \"cwiî kan ay teqqimen, lemmer, s tidep, day tessinem"
  23,115,"Day t$ilem Nxelq ikwen, kan, di rrayaâ; ar ur d teppu$alem $uône£"
  23,116,"Ay Meqqweô Öebbi, Agellid, Tidep! Ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa, Mass n usgeld ukyis"
  23,117,"Win inaâôen, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, ur isâi ppbut fellas, aqeîîi s ar Mass is kan. Ih, ur rebêen ara ijehliyen"
  23,118,"Ini: \"a Mass iw! Semmeê u Ëun. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun"
  24,1,"Tasurep, Nessader ip id, Nêeppem ip id; Nessader ed, degs, issekniyen iberrzen, amar a d temmektim"
  24,2,"Tin ne$ win iznan, jekwvet, yal yiwen segsen, tawinest iberdan; ur kwen p$aven $ef udem n Öebbi, ma tellam tumnem s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Arbaâ n lmumnin, ad yili d anagi uâaqeb nnsen"
  24,3,"Win iznan ur ippa$ siwa tin iznan, ne$ tamcarekt. Tin iznan ur p ippa$ siwa win iznan, ne$ amcarek. Ipwagdel waya i lmumnin"
  24,4,"Wid itehmen tiâaôviyin, d$a ur d bbwin kué inagan, jekwvet pen îamet iberdan; ur qeblet ccada nnsen, d awez$i. Widen d iballa$en"
  24,5,"Kkes ed wid isteôoâen, deffir waya, u xedmen lfayeq. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  24,6,"Wid itehmen tilawin nnsen, ur sâin inagan, siwa iman nnsen, yiwen segsen ad iggal s Öebbi, kué iberdan, ar neppa d bab n tidep"
  24,7,akked ubrid wis smus ar a t Ixzu Öebbi ma iskaddeb
  24,8,"Ur teppuâaqeb tmeîîut, ma teggul s Öebbi, kué iberdan, ar neppa seg wid iskadben"
  24,9,"akked ubrid, wis smus ar fellas zzâaf n Öebbi, ma issawel ed tidep"
  24,10,"A lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S! Öebbi, s tidep, Issuruf, d Bab n ûûwab"
  24,11,"Ih, wid isweûlen tikerkas, d agraw segwen. Ur p$ilit d cceôô i kunwi, xaîi, d lxiô nnwen. Yal yiwen, degsen, ibbwi ayen ibbwi ubekkav. Aâaqeb abarar i win, segsen, i ibbwin amur ameqwôaêan"
  24,12,"A lemmer lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, mi s slan, meyyzen lxiô, deg iman nnsen, u nnan: \"wagi d tikerkas ibanen"
  24,13,"A lemmer d bbwin, fellas, kué inagan! Ma ur d bbwin ara inagan, ar Öebbi, wigi, d ikeddaben"
  24,14,"Lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S, di ddunit akked laxeôt, a ppesâaddim aâaqeb abarar $ef wayen i$ef temcawaôem"
  24,15,"Mi p id teggarem s yilsawen nnwen, u teqqaôen s imawen nnwen ayen ur tessinem, t$ilem d ulac. Neppa, ar Öebbi, d abarar"
  24,16,"Lemmer, mi as teslam, tennam: \"ur a$ issefk ara umeslay $ef waya! Gedha s yiseK! Wagi d acehrir abarar"
  24,17,"Inuba kwen Öebbi ur teppalsem, am akka, d awez$i, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  24,18,"Ipbeggin awen Öebbi issekniyen. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  24,19,"Ih, wid ib$an a d iazel lâaô, ar wid iumnen, fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan di ddunit, di laxeôt. Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem"
  24,20,"A lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S! U Öebbi d Umâin, Ipêunu"
  24,21,"A wid iumnen! Ur teddut di lateô n Cciîan. Win iteddun di lateô n Cciîan, ar la iteddu di lâaô akked tuccva. Lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S, ur ippizdig degwen yiwen, d awez$i. Maca, Öebbi Izzizdig win i S ihwan. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw"
  24,22,"Wid, degwen, iwumi ippunefk lfevl akked terkunt, ur pgalan $ef tikci i llzem, i ime$ban, i wid iunagen deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ad semmêen, ad ssurfen. Day ur têemmlem ara mara awen Isemmeê Öebbi? Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  24,23,"Ih, wid ipqeôôiven tilawin zeddigen, istehzan, iumnen, ad pwaxzun di ddunit, di laxeôt. Fellasen aâaqeb abarar"
  24,24,"Ass ideg ara d cehhden $ef igiten nnsen, ilsawen nnsen, ifassen nnsen, ivaôen nnsen"
  24,25,"assen, ad asen Ifk Öebbi ayen ppalasen, s tidep. Ad éôen ar Öebbi d Tidep ibanen"
  24,26,"Yir tlawin i yir irgazen, yir irgazen i yir tlawin. Tilawin n lâali i irgazen n lâali, irgazen lâali i tlawin n lâali. Wigi ur ppkan deg wayen qqaôen. I nitni, ssmaê akked ôôeéq ukyis"
  24,27,"A wid iumnen! Ur keçmet ixxamen ur nelli nnwen, alamma s tsriê, u alamma tselmem $ef imawlan nnsen. Ppif akka i kunwi, amar a d tesmektim"
  24,28,"Ma ur tufim êedd degsen, ur keçmet alamma s tsriê. Ma nnan awen d: \"u$alet\", u$alet. Yif it wakka i ûûfawa nnwen. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem"
  24,29,"Ulac u$ilif fellawen ma tkecmem ixxamen ur nepwazde$, ma tella t$awsa nnwen degsen. Öebbi Iéôa acu d teqqaôem, u wacu teppeffrem"
  24,30,"Ini i wid iumnen ad brun i wallen nnsen, ad ssôen tuzzuft nnsen. Yif it wakka i ûûfawa nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa ayen xeddmen"
  24,31,"Ini i tid iumnen ad brunt i wallen nnsent, ad ssôent tuzzuft nnsent, ur d sskanent, di zzin nnsent, siwa ayen d ivehôen segs, ad $umment idmaren nnsent. Ur d sskanent ccbuê nnsent, siwa i irgazen nnsent, ne$ ibabaten nnsent, ne$ im$aôen nnsent, ne$ iqcicen nnsent, ne$ irbiben nnsent, ne$ atmaten nnsent, ne$ iqcicen n watmaten nnsent, ne$ wid n tsetmatin nnsent, ne$ tiqeddacin nnsent, ne$ taklatin nnsent, ne$ iqeddacen imudduzen, ne$ arrac ur nelleméi. Ur kkatent dderz, ad ipwassen zzin nnsent uffir. Steôoâet akw i Öebbi, a lmumnin, amar a prebêem"
  24,32,"Jewoet i iâzriyen nnwen, akked wid imaânen seg waklan nnwen, akked teklatin nnwen. Ma d ime$ban ay llan, a ten Iôéeq Öebbi, s lfevl iS. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw"
  24,33,"Wid ur nufa ara ar a$en, ad ûebôen ar ten id Iôéeq Öebbi, s lfevl iS. Wid, seg waklan nnwen, i ib$an ad asen tarum aserreê, arut asen ma teéôam ten, d at lxiô ay llan. Fket asen seg ayla i wen Ifka Öebbi. Ur pêeppimet $ef teklatin nnwen, tiquêbit, i rrbeê nnwen di tmeddurt n ddunit, ma b$ant tezdeg. Ma têeppmen, Öebbi, deffir uêeppem nnsent, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  24,34,"Ni$ Nessader awen ed issekniyen iberrzen, akked umedya n wid iâacen uqbel nnwen, d anabi i wid ipêezziben"
  24,35,"Öebbi d tafat n tmurt akked igenwan. Amedya n tafat iS d takwap degs taftilt. Taftilt daxel n tqeôâap. Taqeôâap, amzun d itri acôaôaq, tecâal it ttejôa iôqan, tazemmurt ur nelli n ugmuv ne$ n utaram. Qôib a pfet zzit is, ur p tennul tmes. Tafat $ef tafat. Ippawi Öebbi win i S ihwan ar tafat iS. Ippak ed Öebbi imedyaten i medden. Öebbi Iéôa yal cci"
  24,36,"Deg ixxamen i Ib$a Öebbi ad ufraren, ideg ara d immekti yisem iS, sbuccuâen T ssbeê, tameddit"
  24,37,"Irgazen ur tes$afal ttjaôa, ne$ ssuq, $ef usmekti n Öebbi, $ef téallit, $ef zzakat; ppagwaden ass, ideg ara nehwwalen wallen akked wulawen"
  24,38,"Iwakken a ten Ikafi Öebbi $ef wayen xeddmen d amxallef, ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. Öebbi Ip$iti win i S ihwan, war aktili"
  24,39,"Igiten n wid ijehlen, am aylal deg uza$aô. Win ifuden, ad i$il d aman. Alamma mi ibbwev $uôes, ur ippaf acemma. A n iaf Öebbi, Issuli as leêsab is. Öebbi Ip$awal deg uqeîîi"
  24,40,"Ne$ am tillas di yill le$miq. T$umm it lmuja, sufella lmuja, sufella asigna. Tillas sennig tiyav. Ma issuffe$ ed afus is, ur issawev a t iwali. Win iwumi ur Iga ara Öebbi tafat, ur isâi tafat"
  24,41,"Day ur twalav ara, sbuccuâen Öebbi i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ifrax deg waffug. Issen taéallit akked usbuccaâ n yal yiwen. Öebbi Iéôa ayen xeddmen"
  24,42,N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. £uô öÖebbi tu$alin
  24,43,"Ur twalav ara Öebbi Isselêay asigna, sinna, a t Izdi, sinna, a t Issem$weô? D$a a pwaliv ageffur a d iffe$ si zdaxel is. Isrusu d, seg idurar igenni, abruri. Ad Iwwet yis, win i S ihwan, a t Iveôôef $ef win i S ihwan. Tafat n lebôaq iS qôib a ppeglu s yiéôi"
  24,44,"Öebbi Ismizwar iv akked wass. Deg wayagi, s tidep, d aselmed i wid isâan iéôi"
  24,45,"Öebbi Ixleq akw lêayawan, seg waman. Garasen, illa win ippeênunufen $ef uâabbuv is, win ileêêun $ef sin ivaôôen, win ileêêun $ef kué. Ixelleq Öebbi ayen i S ihwan. Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci"
  24,46,"Ni$ Nessader ed issekniyen iberrzen. Öebbi Inehhu win i S ihwan, ar ubrid uwqim"
  24,47,"Qqaôen: \"numen s Öebbi akked Umazan, nu$ awal\". Sinna, deffir waya, iwexxeô urbaâ segsen. Wigi ur llin d lmumnin"
  24,48,"Mi pwanecden ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad Iêudd garasen, arbaâ segsen iwexxeô"
  24,49,"Ma sâan lêeqq, a d asen $uôes, d imvuâen"
  24,50,"Day helken wulawen nnsen, ne$ cukken, ne$ ugaden a ten Isneêyaf Öebbi akked Umazan iS? Xaîi, widak d imednas"
  24,51,"Timenna n lmumnin, mara ssutren aêuddu n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad Iêudd garasen, d tigi kan: \"nesla, nôuva\". D wigi ay d imerbaê"
  24,52,"Win iôuvan Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ippagwaden Öebbi, ipêezziben, nitni d isaâdiyen"
  24,53,"Ggulen s Öebbi, tagallit meqqwôen, ar ma tumôev asen, ard ad ff$en, war ccekk. Ini: \"ur pgallat, annuz ipwassen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa ayen txeddmem"
  24,54,"Ini: \"ôavit Öebbi, ôavit Amazan\". Ma wexxôen, fellas, neppa, ayen kan i s sbabben, fellawen kunwi ayen i wen sbabben. Ma tôuvam T, a ppeppwanhum. I iwatan i Umazan, siwa awal ipbegginen"
  24,55,"Iâahed Öebbi, i wid iumnen segwen, u xedmen ayen ilhan, ara ten Irr, war ccekk, d igensas di tmurt, akken Irra wid i ten id izwaren; ara ad asen Isseqâad ddin nnsen i$ef i ten Iôuva; ar ad asen Issegwri laman, deffir tugdi. Âabden iyI, ur iyI pcaraken acemma. Wid ijehlen, deffir waya, widak d iballa$en"
  24,56,"Beddet i téallit, zekkit, a$et awal i Umazan. Amar aêunu fellawen"
  24,57,£uôwat a p$ilem wid ijehlen sfunnugen di tmurt. Axxam nnsen d times. A tu$alin tucmip
  24,58,"A wid iumnen! S uâammed nnwen ara d kecmen, $uôwen, waklan nnwen akw wid, degwen, ur nebli$ ara, krav iberdan ideg ur telsim ara: uqbel taéallit n tafrara, $ef îîhuô mara tekksem iceîîiven, deffir téallit n lâica. Ulac u$ilif fellawen ne$ fellasen, ma wa iéuô wa, deffir lewqat agi. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab"
  24,59,"Ma bel$en warrac nnwen, s uâammed nnwen, am wid i ten id izwaren. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen iS. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab"
  24,60,"Ulac u$ilif $ef tâuqaô i iâaddan i jwao, ma kksent iceîîiven nnsent, mebla ma sseknent ccbuê nnsent. Ma setêant, yif it i nitenti. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw"
  24,61,"Ur telli tiyta deg uder$al, ne$ deg urejdal, ne$ deg umuvin, ne$ degwen, ma teççam deg ixxamen nnwen, deg wid n ibabaten nnwen, deg wid n tyimmatin nnwen, deg wid n watmaten nnwen, deg wid n tsetmatin nnwen, deg wid iâammiten nnwen, deg wid n tâammitin nnwen, deg wid ixaliten nnwen, deg wid n txaltitin nnwen, deg wid ideg tesâam tisura, ar uêbib nnwen. Ulac u$ilif fellawen ma teççam d agraw, ne$ d ifôiden. Mara tkecmen ixxamen, msalamet s wazul iôqan, aêmayan, s$uô Öebbi. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen. Amar a pfehmem"
  24,62,"Lmumnin, siwa wid iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma llan yides $ef lameô iten icerken, ur pôuêun alamma ssutren as tsriê. Ih, wid i k issuturen tsriê, d nitni i iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma ssutren ak tsriê, $ef kra iten iaânan, serreê i win i k ihwan, segsen. Ssuter i Öebbi ad sen Isemmeê. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  24,63,"Ur êepbet asiwwel garawen i Umazan, am mara temsawalem. Ih, Iéôa Öebbi wid, segwen, ippensaren s tuffra. Ad steêdren wid mgirrden lameô iS: ad ppuhewwlen, ne$ ad sâaddin aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  24,64,"Ih, day maççi n Öebbi, i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ni$ Iéôa amek tellam $uôeS. Ass n tu$alin nnsen $uôeS, ad asen Imel d acu xedmen. Öebbi Issen yal cci"
  25,1,"Ad Iôqu Win id Issadren afraz, i umdan iS, iwakken ad yili d aneddaô imavalen"
  25,2,"Win Ilan tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan; ur Isâi mmi S; ur aS illi ucrik di tgelda. Ixleq yal cci, Iwezn it s lmizan"
  25,3,"Ddmen, war Neppa, iôebbiten ur nexliq acemma. D nitni i ipwaxelqen. Ur pseyyin vveô ne$ aba$uô, i iman nnsen. Ur pseyyin di tmeppant ne$ di tmeddurt, ne$ di tnekra"
  25,4,"Nnan wid ijehlen: \"ayagi, d tikerkas kan. Isnulfa tent id, iâawen it, fellas, ugdud nniven. Ni$ densen u skaddben"
  25,5,"Nnan: \"d timucuha imezwura, i iura; qqaôen as tent ûûbeê, tameddit"
  25,6,"Ini: \"Issader it id, Win Issnen sser n tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, s tidep, Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  25,7,"Nnan: \"d acut Umazan agi i iteppen lqut, iteddun ar leswaq? A lemmer id irs $uôes lmelk, ara yilin yides d aneddaô"
  25,8,"ne$ ippunefk as ugerruj, ne$ isâa aqwiô itepp segs\"! Nnan imednas: \"la teppeddum kan d urgaz iwumi sseêren"
  25,9,"Wali amek id ppaken fellak imedyaten. Nnetlafen, ur zmiren ad pwanhun"
  25,10,"Ad Iôqu Win ad ak Ifken, ma Irad, i ifen ayagi: leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Ad ak Issali lebôuo"
  25,11,"Xaîi, nekôen imir. Nhegga d times i win inekôen imir"
  25,12,"Mi ten twala si tama ibaâden, ad as slen s leêôaôa akked zzhir"
  25,13,"Mara $lin degs, nitni pwarzen deg umekkan uqmiv, ad siwlen, dinna, i wangar"
  25,14,"Ur ssawalet ara, assa, i yiwet n wangar, ssiwlet i waîas n wangaren"
  25,15,"Ini: \"ppif ayagi, ne$ Loennet n lebda i Nâahed i wid ipêezziben? D neppat ay d arraz, ay d taggara, i nitni"
  25,16,"I nitni degs, ayen i sen ihwan, i lebda. D lemâahda i$ef Iuksan Mass ik"
  25,17,"Ass ideg ara ten Ifser, nitni akked wid âabden, war Öebbi, ad Yini: \"d kunwi i itelfen imdanen iW agi, ne$ d nitni i iff$en abrid"
  25,18,"A d inin: \"gedha s yiseK! Ur a$ issefk a neddu d bab, war Keçç. Maca, T$atev ten, nitni akked imezwura nnsen, armi ppun asmekti, u$alen d agdud ixeûôen"
  25,19,"Atan nekôen kwen $ef wayen d tennam. Ihi ur tezmirem i tsensert, ne$ i leslak. Win idensen, degwen, a Nessukk fellas, aâaqeb ameqwôan"
  25,20,"Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, imazanen, mebla ma llan teppen lqut, u teddun ar leswaq. Nerra kwen, wa ihewwel wa, ma a pûebôem. Mass ik Izga la d Ismuqul"
  25,21,"Nnan wid ur nessarem ara timlilit yidne£: \"a lemmer id ssersen lmalayek $uône$, ne$ nwala Mass nne$\"! Ni$ sme$wôen aîas iman nnsen, u ffuhrin aîas"
  25,22,"Ass ideg ara walin lmalayek, ur ippili wassen d abecceô ibe$wviyen, s lxiô. A d inin: d aêdid ur nepwazgar"
  25,23,"Nezzi $eô igiten nnsen, Nerra ten d a$ebbaô immebruzzâen"
  25,24,"Imawlan n Loennet, assen, di tnezdu$t akked trusi iufraren"
  25,25,"Ass ideg ara iceqqeq igenni s usigna, ideg ara d ssersen lmalayek, ta deffir ta"
  25,26,"tagelda, assen, tidep, i Uênin. D ass uwâiô i ijehliyen"
  25,27,"Ass ideg ara i$eéé umednus ifassen is, ad yini: \"a yamxix iw, a lemmer ddi$ d ubrid Umazan"
  25,28,"A tawa$it pwa$e$, a lemmer ur rri$ ara winnat d aêbib"
  25,29,"Ni$ itelf iyi seg usmekti i illan iusa yi d. Cciîan, i umdan, izga d axeddaâ"
  25,30,"Inna Umazan: \"a Mass iw! Ar ugdud iw, s tidep, Leqwôan agi d askeôfeé"
  25,31,"Akka, i yal nnbi, Nefka acengu seg ibe$wviyen. Iqadd Mass ik, i nnhaya akked usellek"
  25,32,"Nnan wid ijehlen: \"a lemmer i s d ssersen Leqwôan, deg yiwet n tikelt\"! Akka, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yis. Nesemderri t d idurra"
  25,33,"Ur ak d ppawin amedya, mebla ma Nuzen ak d tidep, akked ufesser amxallef"
  25,34,"Wid ara ipwafesren af udmawen nnsen, ar Loahennama, widak d at umkan n dir mavi, d at ubrid im$eôôeq mavi"
  25,35,"Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa, u Nerna $uôes gma s, Haôun, d am²âiwen"
  25,36,"Nenna: \"ôuêet ar ugdud i inekôen issekniyen nne£\". Nhudd iten qeccuc meccuc"
  25,37,"Agdud n Nuê, mi nekôen imazanen, Ne$ves iten, u Nerra ten d assekni i medden. Nhegga i imednas aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  25,38,"Âad, Tamud, At Öôas, u aîas isuta garasen"
  25,39,"I yal wa, Nefka imedyaten. Yal wa, Neôéa t wakali"
  25,40,"Ni$ âaddan $ef taddart i$ef id i$li ugeffur ageswaê. Day qqimen ur p walan ara? Xaîi, ur ssaramen ara tanekra"
  25,41,"Mi k walan, ppemsexxiôen kan fellak: \"day d wagi id Iuzen Öebbi, d Amazan"
  25,42,"Qôib i $ itlef seg iôebbiten nne$, lemmer ur neûbiô fellasen\". Deqqal ad éôen mara walin aâaqeb, anwa i innetlafen, kteô, seg ubrid"
  25,43,"Twalav win i irran lhawiyya s d ôebbi s? Day ad as tiliv, keçç, d awkil"
  25,44,"Day t$ilev tegwti, segsen, sellen ne$ fehmen? Nitni am lmal kan, aâer $elben ten akken nnetlafen seg ubrid"
  25,45,"Ma twalav Mass ik, amek id Ifka tili? Lemmer i S ihwi, Irra p d tusbiî. D$a Nefka yas itij d ppbut"
  25,46,"Sinna, Njebd ip id $uône£, ajbad isehlen"
  25,47,"D Neppa i wen Irran iv d aceîîiv, ives d areyyeê, u Irra ass d tanekra"
  25,48,"D Neppa i wen d Iuznen avu, d abecceô s uêunu S. Nessers ed, seg igenni, aman iûfan"
  25,49,"iwakken a Neêyu yissen tamurt immuten; a Nessew yissen aîas seg wid id Nexleq n lmal, akked imdanen"
  25,50,"Ni$ Nfeôq iten garasen, iwakken a d mmektin. Tegwti n yimdanen ugin; atnan kan di tijehli"
  25,51,"Lemmer i £ ihwi, yili Nuzen aneddaô, i yal tamdint"
  25,52,"Ur ppa$ awal i ijehliyen. Nna$ iten yis, amennu$ ameqwôan"
  25,53,"D Neppa i Issemfaôaqen sin ilellen, yiwen êlaw, d aéidan, wayev ôéag, d ameô$an. Irra, garasen, agadir, aêdid ur nepwazgar"
  25,54,"D Neppa i Ixelqen amdan seg waman. Ifka yas laâmum, lexwal. Mass ik Izga d Win Izemren"
  25,55,"La âabden, war Öebbi, ayen ur ten inefâan, ur ten ivuôôen. Ajehli, ar loiha n Mass is, izga d win issefôa$en"
  25,56,"Nuzen ik id kan, i ubecceô d uneddeô"
  25,57,"Ini: \"ur awen ssutre$, $ef waya, kra n teqdiât. Ssutre$ kan, i win ib$an, ad ia$ abrid $eô Mass is"
  25,58,Ppkel $ef Umuddir ur Nepmeppat. Sbuccaâ iT s ccekôan. Iqadd i tussna ibekkaven n imdanen iS
  25,59,"I Ixelqen tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan. Sinna, Aênin Iâannec af usgeld. Steqsi w iT issnen"
  25,60,"Ma pwanecden: \"knut i Uênin\"! A d rren: \"d acu T Uênin? Day a neknu i w ara $ d tamôev\"? D a$unfu i sen irna"
  25,61,"Ad Iôqu Win Irran itran deg igenni. Irna degs, lefnaô, akked waggur bu tziri"
  25,62,"D Neppa i Irran iv akked wass mestebâan, i win ib$an ad ismekti, ne$ ib$an ad isnemmer"
  25,63,"Ixdimen n Uênin, i ileêêun di tmurt di lehna, ma numren ten at war tussna, qqaôen: \"tifrat"
  25,64,"I ippaâwazen i Mass nnsen, knan ne$ bedden"
  25,65,"I iqqaôen: \"a Mass nne$! Veôôef segne$ aâaqeb n Loahennama. Ih, aâaqeb is ipwaêeppem"
  25,66,"Neppat, s tidep, d tadirant, i tnezdu$t akked i$imi"
  25,67,"Wid, ma seôôfen, ur veggiâen, ur pcuêêun: igi iwulmen atan garasen"
  25,68,"Wid ur nenâaô ôebbi nniven, ar tama n Öebbi. Ur neqqen amdan, d ayen Igdel Öebbi, siwa $ef tidep. Ur zennun. Win ixedmen ayagi, ibbwi ibekkaven"
  25,69,"Ad ippuâaqeb berdayen, ass n tnekra. Ad iwekkeô d imdelli"
  25,70,"siwa win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I wigi, ad Inûef Öebbi tucmitin nnsen, s yise$iyen. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  25,71,"Win isteôoâen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ihi, iutub Öebbi s ppuba n tidep"
  25,72,"Wid ur ncehhed ccada n rrya; u, ma mmugren tifukal, ddan d ukyisen"
  25,73,"Wid, mara asen d smmektin issekniyen n Mass nnsen, ur d neggar tiâéegt ne$ tider$elt fellasen"
  25,74,"Wid iqqaôen: \"a Mass nne$! Err tilawin nne$, akked dderya nne$, d ssuâada n wallen. Err ane$ d wid inehhun wid ipêezziben"
  25,75,"Widak ad ppuoazin s t$uôfatin, ilmend n wayen ûebôen. Ad magren, dinna, azul, tifrat"
  25,76,"Dinna, ad wekkôen, d amkan amxalef i tnezdu$t d i$imi"
  25,77,"Ini: \"ur d Irezzu Mass iw, degwen, ma ur tnujem $uôeS. Ni$ tnekôem? Ad iu$al waya d ayen ilezmen"